Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}旧金山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大卫森宠物店{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好，麦克古德太太 - 好，丹尼尔斯小姐{\r}\NHello, Mrs. MacGruder. Oh, hello, Miss Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有见过这么多海鸥吗？ 想是怎么回事？{\r}\NHave you ever seen so many gulls? What do you suppose it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一定是海上有暴风雨 把它们赶往内陆了{\r}\NThere must be a storm at sea. That can drive them inland, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还希望会晚点过来 鸟还没送到呢{\r}\NI was hoping you'd be a little late. You see, he hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 但说三点的 - 我知道{\r}\N- Oh, but you said 3:00. - Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道，我打了一早的电话{\r}\NI know. I've been calling all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐，有所不知{\r}\NOh, Miss Daniels, you have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们很难弄到手，真的{\r}\NThey are so difficult to get. Really, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们得从印度进口雏鸟，然后…{\r}\NWe have to get them from India, when they're just baby chicks, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这只不是雏鸟吧？{\r}\NThis one won't be a chick, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然不是 这只是成年的八哥鸟{\r}\NCertainly not. Oh, no, certainly not. This will be a full-grown mynah bird. Full-grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 它会说话？ - 它当然会…{\r}\NAnd he'll talk? Well, yes, of course he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，得教它说话{\r}\NWell, no, you'll have to teach him to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最好再打通电话 他们说三点会到{\r}\NI guess maybe I'd better phone. They said 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可能是塞车吧，我联络看看{\r}\NMaybe it's the traffic. I'll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 能稍等一下吗？ - 还是把鸟送到我家吧{\r}\NWould you mind waiting? Well, maybe you'd better deliver him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我给我家的地址{\r}\NLet me give you my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那好吧{\r}\NOh, well, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我确定他们在路上了{\r}\Nbut I'm sure they're on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能打通电话吗？{\r}\NWould you mind if I called?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请便{\r}\NNo. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 请帮个忙 - 什么？{\r}\NI wonder if you could help me. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说请帮个忙{\r}\NI said, I wonder if you could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是，你想找什么，先生？ - 爱情鸟{\r}\NYes. What is it you're looking for, sir? Lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱情鸟？{\r}\NLovebirds, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，我听说那有分很多种类{\r}\NYes. I understand there are different varieties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是真的吗？ - 真的{\r}\NIs that true? Well, yes, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是要给我妹妹当生日礼物的{\r}\NWell, these are for my sister for her birthday, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她才11岁 所以我不想买一对{\r}\Nand as she's only gonna be 11, I wouldn't want a pair of birds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过于热情的鸟{\r}\Nthat were too demonstrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我完全理解{\r}\NI understand completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我也不想买一对太冷淡的鸟{\r}\NAt the same time, I wouldn't want them to be too aloof, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然不了{\r}\NNo, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}店里有相敬如宾的一对小鸟吗？{\r}\NDo you happen to have a pair of birds that are just friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该有，我找找看{\r}\NOh, I think so. Now, then, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些不是爱情鸟吗？{\r}\NAren't those lovebirds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，那些是红鸟{\r}\NNo. Those are red birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我以为它们是红雀{\r}\NI thought they were strawberry finches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，我们也这样称呼它们{\r}\NYes. We call them that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找到了，爱情鸟{\r}\NHere we are. Lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是金丝雀{\r}\NThose are canaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不觉得自己很糟糕吗？{\r}\NDoesn't this make you feel awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么很糟糕…{\r}\NDoesn't what make me feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把这些可怜无辜的小东西 关在笼子里？{\r}\NHaving all these poor, little innocent creatures caged up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们总不能 让它们在店里飞来飞去吧{\r}\NWell, we can't just let them fly around the shop, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然不能{\r}\NNo, I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么鸟类学上的原因 必须把它们隔开吗？{\r}\NIs there an ornithological reason for keeping them in separate cages?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有，为了保护品种{\r}\NWell, certainly. It's to protect the species.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，那很重要 尤其是在换毛期的时候{\r}\NYes, that's important, especially during the molting season.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是特别危险的时期{\r}\NThat's a particularly dangerous time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 它们正在换毛吗？ - 一部分是{\r}\NAre they molting now? Oh, some of them are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么知道？{\r}\NHow can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们会垂头丧气的{\r}\NWell, they get a sort of hangdog expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了，那爱情鸟呢？{\r}\NYes, I see. Well, what about the lovebirds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你确定不看看金丝雀？{\r}\NAre you sure you wouldn't like to see a canary instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们这周进了些很美的金丝雀{\r}\NWe have some very nice canaries this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧{\r}\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，我能看看吗？{\r}\NAll right. May I see it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了？{\r}\NOh, what is it? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抓到了{\r}\NThere we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好险 - 太好了{\r}\N- Oh, there. - Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回的金牢笼吧 梅兰妮丹尼尔斯{\r}\NBack in your gilded cage, Melanie Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说什么？{\r}\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是在打比喻，丹尼尔斯小姐{\r}\NI was merely drawing a parallel, Miss Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你怎么知道我的名字？ - 小鸟告诉我的{\r}\NHow did you know my name? A little birdie told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见，丹尼尔斯小姐、女士{\r}\NGood day, Miss Daniels. Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}慢着，我不认识你{\r}\NHey, wait a minute. I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 但我认识 - 怎么说？{\r}\NAh, but I know you. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们在法庭上见过 - 我们未曾在法庭上见过{\r}\NWe met in court. We never met in court or anyplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错，我换个说法 我在法庭看过{\r}\NThat's true. I'll rephrase it. I saw you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么时候？{\r}\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不记得因为的恶作剧{\r}\NDon't you remember one of your practical jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}使得一扇玻璃窗被打破了吗？{\r}\Nthat resulted in the smashing of a plate-glass window?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我没有打破窗户 - 但是恶作剧害的{\r}\NI didn't break that window. Yes, but your little prank did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 法官真该把关进大牢 - 你是谁，警察吗？{\r}\NThe judge should've put you behind bars. What are you, a policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不太相信法律，丹尼尔斯小姐 我也不太喜欢恶作剧{\r}\NI merely believe in the law, Miss Daniels. And I'm not too keen on practical jokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那你的爱情鸟故事… - 我是真的想买爱情鸟{\r}\NWhat do you call your lovebird story if not... Oh, I really wanted the lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你明知道我不是店员，你故意…{\r}\NWell, you knew I didn't work here. You deliberately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，我一进门就认出了{\r}\NRight. I recognized you when I came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是想让知道 当被整的一方是什么感受{\r}\NI just thought you might like to know what it's like to be on the other end of a gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有什么感想？ - 我认为你是个坏蛋{\r}\NWhat do you think of that? I think you're a louse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是 再见，丹尼尔斯小姐、女士{\r}\NI am. Good day, Miss Daniels. Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真庆幸你没买到爱情鸟{\r}\NAnd I'm glad you didn't get your lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会去别的地方买，法庭上见了{\r}\NOh, I'll find something else. See you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那个人是谁？ - 我不知道{\r}\NWho was that man? I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们说 八哥鸟今天下午就会送到{\r}\NThey said the mynah bird would be here later this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}若愿意再过来一趟{\r}\Nif you care to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，送到我家吧{\r}\NNo, you'd better send him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 能借用电话吗？ - 请便{\r}\NMay I use this phone? Why, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}《每日新闻报》？ 我是 梅兰妮丹尼尔斯，请转地方新闻部{\r}\NDaily News? It's Melanie Daniels. Could you get me the City Desk, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请留步，麦克古德太太{\r}\NJust a minute, Mrs. MacGruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好，查理，我是梅兰妮{\r}\NHello, Charlie. Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要请你帮个忙{\r}\NI want you to do a favor for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，只是个小忙{\r}\NNo, this is a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给你压力？ 亲爱的查理 我怎么会给你压力？{\r}\NPressure you? Why, Charlie, darling, would I try to pressure you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能替我致电汽车监理所吗？{\r}\NWould you call the Department of Motor Vehicles for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找出这个车牌的车主{\r}\NFind out who owns this license plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-J-H-0-0-3 W-J-H-0-0-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，加州车牌{\r}\NYes, a California plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我等会就过去 爸爸在办公室吗？{\r}\NNo. I'll stop off in a little while. Is Daddy in his office?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我不想打断会议 告诉他我晚点去找他{\r}\NNo, I don't want to break in on a meeting. Tell him I'll see him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，查理{\r}\NThank you, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}店里有爱情鸟吗？{\r}\NDo you have any lovebirds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，店里没有 但我可以替订购{\r}\NWell, no, not in the shop, but I can order them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 多快会到？ - 什么时候要？{\r}\NHow soon? Well, when would you want them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}立刻{\r}\NImmediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天早上应该就能送到{\r}\NWell, I could probably have them here by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那样可以吗？ - 当然可以{\r}\NWould that be all right? That would be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契尔班纳先生收{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 小姐，这是要给米契班纳的？ - 对{\r}\NMiss, is that for Mitch Brenner? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他不在家 - 没关系{\r}\NHe's not home. That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果要送小鸟给他 他要周一才会回来{\r}\NHe won't be back until Monday, I mean, if those birds are for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 周一？ - 是{\r}\N- Monday? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想不该把小鸟留在走廊上吧？{\r}\NI don't think you should leave them in the hall, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那…他去哪了？{\r}\NWell... Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}博德加湾 他每个周末都会去那里{\r}\NBodega Bay. He goes there every weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}博德加湾在哪里？{\r}\NBodega Bay. Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}沿着海岸往北走约一百公里{\r}\NUp the coast, about 60 miles north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一百公里…{\r}\NSixty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走高速公路约一个半小时的车程 走海岸公路则要两小时{\r}\NIt's an hour and a half by freeway, or two hours if you take the Coast Highway. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我愿意照顾小鸟 但我也要出远门{\r}\NI'd look after them myself, but I'm going away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很抱歉{\r}\NI'm awfully sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邮局-  日用品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}五金- 杂货{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 早安 - 早安{\r}\N- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想请你帮个忙 - 我尽量{\r}\NI wonder if you could help me. I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要找米契尔班纳{\r}\NI'm looking for a man named Mitchell Brenner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你认识他吗？ - 认识{\r}\N- Do you know him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他住在哪里？ - 博德加湾{\r}\N- Where does he live? - Right here, Bodega Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 博德加湾的哪里？ - 海湾对面{\r}\NYes, I know, but where? Right across the bay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哪里？{\r}\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看见我指的方向了？ - 是{\r}\NNow, see where I'm pointing? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看见那两棵大树了？{\r}\NSee them two big trees across there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 海湾的另一边吗？ 看见了 - 那栋白色房子？{\r}\NOn the other side of the bay? Yes. - And the white house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是 - 那就是班纳家了{\r}\N- Yes. That's where the Brenners live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班纳家？ 班纳夫妇的家？{\r}\NThe Brenners? Mr. and Mrs. Brenner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不，只有莉迪雅和两个孩子 - 两个孩子？{\r}\NNo. Just Lydia and the two kids. The two kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，米契和小女儿{\r}\NYeah, Mitch and the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我懂了，我要怎么过去？{\r}\NOh, I see. How do I get down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}沿着海湾边的路走 就能走到他们家大门口{\r}\NYou follow the road around the bay, and that'll take you right to their front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大门口，我能走小路吗？{\r}\NThe front door. Is there a back road I can take?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不，只有那条路 - 我想给他们惊喜{\r}\NNo. That's the only road. You see, I want to surprise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不想让他们看见我 - 这样{\r}\NI don't want them to see me arrive. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是惊喜{\r}\NIt's a surprise, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可以乘船穿过海湾 到他们家的码头{\r}\NWell, you could get yourself a boat and cut right across the bay to their dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要去哪租船？{\r}\NWhere would I get a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}下方的海潮餐厅{\r}\NDown by the Tides Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 曾开过船吗？ - 当然{\r}\NDid you ever handle an outboard boat? Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我替叫船吧？ - 谢谢{\r}\NWant me to order one for you? Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 的名字？ - 丹尼尔斯{\r}\N- What name? - Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你能否告诉我… - 请稍等一下{\r}\NI wonder if you could tell me... Yeah. Just hold it a minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 小女儿的名字？ - 班纳家的小女儿？{\r}\NThe little girl's name? The little Brenner girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是 - 应该是爱丽丝吧{\r}\NYes. Alice, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈利，班纳家的小女儿 叫什么名字？{\r}\NHarry, what's the little Brenner girl's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 露薏丝 - 爱丽丝吗？{\r}\N- Lois. - Alice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不，是露薏丝 - 是爱丽丝{\r}\NNo, it's Lois. It's Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你确定吗？{\r}\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不敢保证 如果是想问这个{\r}\NWell, I'm not positive, if that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我需要她的真名{\r}\NI need her exact name, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请再稍等一下{\r}\NOh, just hold on one more minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样的话，我教怎么做{\r}\NIn that case, I'll tell you what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一路穿过镇上 会看见左手边有一间小旅馆{\r}\NYou go straight through town till you see a little hotel on your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后右转{\r}\NThen you turn right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 记好了？ - 是{\r}\N- Now, you got that? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在靠近山顶处 会看见一所学校，再过去{\r}\NNear the top of the hill, you'll see the school, and just beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一间信箱是红色的房子{\r}\Na little house with a red mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那里是安妮海沃斯老师的家{\r}\NThat's where Annie Hayworth, the schoolteacher, lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 可以问她班纳家小女儿的事 - 谢谢{\r}\NYou ask her about the little Brenner girl. Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}替自己省点麻烦吧 我确定她叫爱丽丝{\r}\NSave yourself a lot of trouble. Name's Alice for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我20分钟后能搭船吗？{\r}\NCan I have the boat in about 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 电话费要多少？ - 不用了{\r}\NHow much for the phone calls? Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}博德加湾学校{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是谁？ - 我{\r}\NWho is it? Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“我” 是谁？{\r}\NWho's "me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 海沃斯小姐？ - 是{\r}\N- Miss Hayworth? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是梅兰妮丹尼尔斯 抱歉打扰了…{\r}\NI'm Melanie Daniels. I'm sorry to bother you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有事吗？ - 邮局的人要我来找{\r}\NYes? The man at the post office sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说知道班纳家小女儿的名字{\r}\NHe said you could tell me the name of the little Brenner girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西？{\r}\NCathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她住在海湾对面那间白色房子？{\r}\NThe one who lives in the white house across the bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没错，凯西班纳 - 他很确定是爱丽丝或露薏丝{\r}\NThat's the one. Cathy Brenner. He seemed sure it was either Alice or Lois.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以这镇上的信 永远送不到对的地方{\r}\NWhich is why the mail never gets delivered to the right place in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 抱歉，要抽烟吗？ - 谢谢{\r}\NI'm sorry. Smoke? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找凯西有事吗？{\r}\NDid you want to see Cathy about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么事{\r}\NWell, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是米契的朋友？{\r}\NAre you a friend of Mitch's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不算是{\r}\NNo, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我20分钟前就想抽烟了{\r}\NYou know, I've been wanting a cigarette for the last 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我一直闲不下来{\r}\NI just couldn't convince myself to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}翻土这件事会让人停不下来{\r}\NThis tilling of the soil can become compulsive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这花园很漂亮{\r}\NIt's a very pretty garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢 这是度过空闲时间的好方法{\r}\NOh, thank you. Well, it's something to do in your spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在博德加湾，空闲时间可多了{\r}\NThere's a lot of spare time in Bodega Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打算久留吗？{\r}\NAre you planning on staying long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，只待几个小时{\r}\NNo, just a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}见过凯西后就要离开？{\r}\NThen you're leaving after you see Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}差不多{\r}\NWell, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，我无意 把自己搞得神秘兮兮的{\r}\NI'm sorry. I don't mean to sound so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不关我的事{\r}\NActually, it's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最好该出发了{\r}\NWell, I better be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 非常谢谢 - 不客气{\r}\N- Thank you very much. - Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从旧金山 沿海岸公路开车过来？{\r}\NDid you drive up from San Francisco by the coast road?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 风景很棒吧 - 很漂亮{\r}\NNice drive. It's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们在旧金山认识的？{\r}\NIs that where you met Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想大家都是 在那里认识米契的{\r}\NI guess that's where everyone meets Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海沃斯小姐，换神秘兮兮了{\r}\NNow you sound a bit mysterious, Miss Hayworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是吗？{\r}\NDo I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我无意这么做 事实上，我没什么秘密{\r}\NI don't mean to. Actually, I'm an open book, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或者该说我高深莫测{\r}\NOr, rather, a closed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 真漂亮，这是什么鸟？ - 爱情鸟{\r}\NOh, pretty. What are they? Lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了 祝好运，丹尼尔斯小姐{\r}\NI see. Good luck, Miss Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢，我可以走这边吗？{\r}\NThank you. Can I get out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}右转吧 那会带回大马路上{\r}\NGo right around. It'll take you back to the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海沃斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西收{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海潮餐厅- 快艇出租{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 丹尼尔斯小姐的船准备好了？ - 是的{\r}\NDo you have a boat for Miss Daniels?\NYes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是下方那一艘{\r}\NIt's the one right below.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.41,0:25:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没事吧？ - 我没事{\r}\N- Are you all right? - Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.87,0:25:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 它怎么会攻击我？ - 那是我见过最吓人的鸟{\r}\NWhat do you suppose made it do that? That's the damnedest thing I ever saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.92,0:25:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道 它似乎是故意冲向的，流血了{\r}\NI don't know. It seemed to swoop down at you deliberately. Oh, you're bleeding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们去擦药，好吗？{\r}\NLet's take care of that. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乖女孩{\r}\NThat's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.10,0:26:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，怎么了？{\r}\NWhat happened, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 海鸥攻击她 - 海鸥？{\r}\N- Gull hit her. - A gull?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.19,0:26:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去餐厅看看吧{\r}\NLet's try up at the restaurant, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.20,0:26:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可能需要打破伤风针{\r}\NMight need a tetanus shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.66,0:26:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在去年五月出国前 打过预防针了{\r}\NI had a booster before I went abroad last May.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海潮餐厅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.40,0:26:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 怎么了？ - 你好，迪克，这位小姐受伤了{\r}\NWhat happened? Hello, Deke. Young lady cut herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我该找医生吗？ - 不，应该没那么严重，我看看{\r}\NShall I call a doctor? No, I don't think it's that serious. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.28,0:27:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海伦，去拿些棉花和消毒药水{\r}\NHelen, get some cotton and antiseptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小姐，在外头受伤的吗？{\r}\NYou cut yourself outside, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.91,0:27:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别担心，迪克 她在船上受伤的{\r}\NDon't worry, Deke. She did it in a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.41,0:27:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}曾有个男人在停车场摔倒{\r}\NWell, I had a man trip and fall in the parking lot once.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}眼也不眨一下就告我{\r}\NSued me before I could bat an eyelash.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.00,0:27:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐不会告人{\r}\NI don't think Miss Daniels is gonna sue anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.46,0:27:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拿去{\r}\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.17,0:27:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你才是律师 - 谢谢{\r}\NWell, you're the lawyer. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是什么？ - 双氧水{\r}\NWhat's that? Just some peroxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.72,0:27:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来清洗伤口{\r}\NI'll clean out the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.56,0:27:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是律师啊{\r}\NSo you're a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.60,0:27:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错{\r}\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.85,0:27:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我通常是替人辩护 丹尼尔斯小姐，但若我要告人…{\r}\NOf course, I usually defend people, Miss Daniels, but if I were prosecuting...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.23,0:27:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你在这里执业？ - 旧金山，来干嘛？{\r}\NDo you practice here? Uh-uh. San Francisco. What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.07,0:27:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 专攻哪种法律？ - 刑法{\r}\NWhat kind of law? Criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.86,0:27:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以你才想让每个人去坐牢？{\r}\NIs that why you want to see everyone behind bars?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.28,0:27:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是每个人{\r}\NOh, not everyone, Miss Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 只有犯法和恶作剧的人 - 没错{\r}\NOnly violators and practical jokers. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.62,0:27:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\N- Ow! - Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 刚在那里做什么？ - 你没看见爱情鸟？{\r}\NWhat are you doing up here? Didn't you see the lovebirds?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.67,0:27:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是说大老远 替我送爱情鸟过来？{\r}\NOh, you mean, you came all this way to bring me those birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.38,0:28:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟是送给你妹妹的 你说她过生日{\r}\NTo bring your sister those birds. You said it was her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.47,0:28:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 反正我原本就要过来 - 为什么？{\r}\NBesides, I was coming up anyway. What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.60,0:28:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}见我朋友，轻一点{\r}\NTo see a friend of mine. Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.77,0:28:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，的朋友是谁？{\r}\NOh, sorry. Who's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮海沃斯，学校老师{\r}\NAnnie Hayworth, the schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮海沃斯{\r}\NAnnie Hayworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这世界真小{\r}\NWell, small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.61,0:28:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.45,0:28:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么认识安妮？{\r}\NHow do you know Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.66,0:28:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们上同一所大学{\r}\NWe went to school together, college.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.75,0:28:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是吗？ 真想不到 要在这里待多久？{\r}\NDid you? Imagine that. How long are you staying up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个周末{\r}\NThe weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.55,0:28:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}血差不多止住了 按着伤口吧{\r}\NWell, I think the bleeding's almost stopped. Why don't you hold that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.23,0:28:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 来拜访安妮？ - 对{\r}\NSo you came up to see Annie, huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.48,0:28:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想是来看我的{\r}\NI think you came up to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.77,0:29:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我为什么要来看你呢？{\r}\NNow, why would I want to see you of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.61,0:29:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道 但一定是大费周章地{\r}\NI don't know, but you must've gone to a lot of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.32,0:29:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}调查我是谁和我住在哪里{\r}\Nto find out who I was and where I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一点都不麻烦 我只需打给我父亲的报社{\r}\NIt was no trouble at all. I simply called my father's newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.45,0:29:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而且我原本就要过来 我已经说过了{\r}\NBesides, I was coming up anyway. I've already told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.21,0:29:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很喜欢我吧？ - 我讨厌你{\r}\NYou really like me, huh? I loathe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.96,0:29:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没礼貌，既自大又骄傲…{\r}\NYou have no manners. You're arrogant, and conceited, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.96,0:29:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我本来写了封信要给你 但我撕掉了{\r}\NI wrote you a letter about it, in fact, but I tore it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 上头写了什么？ - 不关你的事{\r}\NWhat did it say? None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.47,0:29:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也不喜欢你的海鸥{\r}\NI can't say I like your seagulls much, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.39,0:29:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我大老远过来… - 本来就要过来，记得吗？{\r}\NI come all the way up here to... But you were coming up anyway, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.23,0:29:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契？{\r}\NMitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.40,0:29:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看到你的车子 你到镇上做什么？{\r}\NI thought I saw your car. What are you doing in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.82,0:29:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我来签收货物 - 什么？{\r}\NI had to acknowledge a delivery. Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.49,0:29:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈，这是梅兰妮丹尼尔斯 丹尼尔斯小姐，这是我母亲{\r}\NMother, I'd like you to meet Melanie Daniels. Miss Daniels, my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.66,0:29:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吗？{\r}\NHow do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.33,0:29:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，丹尼尔斯小姐 签收什么？{\r}\NHow do you do, Miss Daniels? Acknowledge a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}货物，丹尼尔斯小姐 从旧金山替我们送小鸟过来{\r}\NA delivery. Miss Daniels brought us some birds from San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.00,0:29:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做为凯西的生日礼物 她在哪里？{\r}\NFor Cathy for her birthday. Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.67,0:30:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她在布林梅尔家{\r}\NAcross at Brinkmeyer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.25,0:30:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上，丹尼尔斯小姐 要在这里过周末{\r}\NAs a matter of fact, Miss Daniels is staying up here for the weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.63,0:30:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以我已邀请她今晚一起用餐{\r}\Nso I've already invited her for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不辞辛劳送那些鸟过来{\r}\NWell, you did go to the trouble of bringing those birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.39,0:30:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么{\r}\NOh, I couldn't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.10,0:30:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你说鸟？ - 对，爱情鸟{\r}\NYou did say birds? Yes, lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了{\r}\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.15,0:30:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以我们可不能 不向道谢就让离开{\r}\NSo we couldn't let you get away without thanking you in some small way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.40,0:30:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还没见到凯西 况且要在这里过周末{\r}\NAnd you haven't met Cathy, and you are staying the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.70,0:30:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是，不过… - 会留下来吧？{\r}\NWell, yes, but... Well, you are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没错，但… - 那就说定了{\r}\NCertainly, but... Then it's all settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.54,0:30:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 晚餐几点开动？ - 七点，一如往常{\r}\NWhat time is dinner, Mother? 7:00, the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.75,0:30:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我会去接，住在哪里？ - 当然是安妮家{\r}\NI'll pick you up. Where are you staying? With Annie, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.59,0:30:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然了，我真笨 6点45分可以吗？{\r}\NOh, of course. How stupid of me. 6:45?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.88,0:30:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮可能另有计划 我得问问看{\r}\NAnnie may have made other plans. I'll have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.43,0:30:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}此外，我自己知道路{\r}\NBesides, I can find my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}确定？ 不会再租船了？{\r}\NYou're sure now? You won't hire a boat or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.80,0:30:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我确定 - 那七点见了{\r}\NI'm sure. 7:00, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许吧{\r}\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.81,0:31:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们会等，头还痛吗？{\r}\NWe'll be waiting for you. How's your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.23,0:31:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好多了，谢谢{\r}\NMuch better, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.27,0:31:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班纳太太，我只是被海鸥弄伤{\r}\NA gull hit me, Mrs. Brenner, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.87,0:31:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 嗨，找到她了？ - 是{\r}\NOh, hi. Did you find her all right? Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.63,0:31:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想问…{\r}\NI was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那块招牌{\r}\NThat sign there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.46,0:31:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}房间出租{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可以在这里住上一晚吗？{\r}\NDo you suppose I could have the room for just a single night?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.51,0:31:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我打算长期出租…{\r}\NI was planning on renting it for a longer time...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.47,0:31:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会很感激{\r}\NI would appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.60,0:31:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我找过镇上其他地方，都客满了{\r}\NI've tried everywhere in town. They're all full.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.97,0:31:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，的行李在车上？{\r}\NWell, all right. Got your bags in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.34,0:31:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我得说真是实际{\r}\NWell, it's utilitarian, I'll say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.52,0:31:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我刚在杂货店 买了一些过夜用品{\r}\NI just picked up some things for the night at the general store.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.53,0:31:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我本来没打算久留{\r}\NYou see, I hadn't planned on staying very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.66,0:31:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道 发生了出乎意料的事？{\r}\NYes, I know. Did something unexpected come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.04,0:32:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，能借用的电话吗？ 我想打电话回家{\r}\NYes. May I use your phone? I'd like to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.33,0:32:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}炉子上有咖啡{\r}\NI just put some coffee on the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.63,0:32:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们都不停止迁徙的？{\r}\NDon't they ever stop migrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好！{\r}\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.19,0:33:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好！{\r}\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.77,0:33:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 丹尼尔斯小姐？ - 是{\r}\NMiss Daniels? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小鸟好漂亮！{\r}\NOh, they're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.57,0:33:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟我想要的一样 那是一只公鸟和一只母鸟吗？{\r}\NThey're just what I wanted. Is there a man and a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.41,0:33:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我都分不清楚 - 应该是{\r}\NI can't tell which is which. Well, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.66,0:33:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好，安妮没安排计划？ - 没有{\r}\NHello there. Annie had no plans, huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.33,0:33:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好，我们很高兴能过来 饿了吗？{\r}\NFine. We're very glad you could come. You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.33,0:33:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 相当饿了 - 晚餐快煮好了{\r}\N- Reasonably. - Dinner's just about ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.67,0:33:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们刚去看鸡{\r}\NWe've been out back looking at the chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们好像有点不对劲{\r}\NSomething seems to be wrong with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些鸡没有不对劲，米契{\r}\NThere's nothing wrong with those chickens, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.09,0:33:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我去打电话给佛莱德布林梅尔 - 那又能怎样？{\r}\NI'm going to call Fred Brinkmeyer right now. What good's that gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.84,0:33:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸡都不吃饲料{\r}\NThe chickens won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是他卖饲料给我的，不是吗？{\r}\NHe sold the feed to me, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.26,0:33:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}买者自负，妈妈 “货物既出恕不退换”{\r}\NCaveat emptor, Mother. "Let the buyer beware."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.39,0:33:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你站在谁那边？{\r}\NWhose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.98,0:33:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我只是在引述法条 - 别管什么法条了{\r}\NMerely quoting the law, dear. Never mind the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.61,0:33:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不会太久，丹尼… 喂，佛莱德？ 我是莉迪雅班纳{\r}\NThis won't take long, Miss... Hello, Fred? Lydia Brenner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.78,0:34:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我没打扰到你吃晚饭吧？ - 喝一杯吗？{\r}\N- I didn't interrupt your dinner, did I? - How about a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.04,0:34:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好的，谢谢 - 佛莱德，你卖给我不好的饲料{\r}\NThank you, I'd love one. Fred, that feed you sold me is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.04,0:34:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸡饲料{\r}\NThe chicken feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.92,0:34:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}品质不好，鸡都不吃{\r}\NWell, it's just no good. The chickens won't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.55,0:34:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸡随时都是饿的{\r}\NThey're always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我到家后，开了一袋饲料 它们连碰都不碰{\r}\NI opened a sack for them when I got home, and they just wouldn't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.72,0:34:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你懂鸡，我也懂 鸡不吃饲料{\r}\NYou know chickens as well as I do, and when they won't eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一定就是饲料有问题，就这样{\r}\Nthere's something wrong with what they're being fed. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.31,0:34:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，它们不是挑嘴鸡{\r}\NNo, they're not fussy chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.31,0:34:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁？ 跟他有何关系？{\r}\NWho? What's he got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.56,0:34:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是你父亲？ - 请坐{\r}\NIs that your father? Mmm-hmm. Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}佛莱德，我不管 你卖了多少袋饲料给他，我的鸡…{\r}\NFred, I don't care how many sacks of feed you sold him. My chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.45,0:34:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了{\r}\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.66,0:34:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹佛西特{\r}\NDan Fawcett.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.08,0:34:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天下午？ 那证实了我的话！ 你卖给我们的饲料…{\r}\NThis afternoon? Well, that just proves what I'm saying! The feed you sold us...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最好去问问他{\r}\NWell, maybe I'd better go over and see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.34,0:35:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不会以为这是什么传染病吧？{\r}\NYou don't think there's something going around, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.26,0:35:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}才不是！{\r}\NNo, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.76,0:35:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，佛莱德 它们没生病，只是不吃饲料{\r}\NNo, Fred, they don't seem sick at all. They just won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.60,0:35:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会去找他，也许他…{\r}\NWell, I'll try to go over and see him. Maybe he...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.03,0:35:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，谢谢{\r}\NAll right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.99,0:35:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹佛西特稍早也打过电话{\r}\NHe had a call from Dan Fawcett a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.54,0:35:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他的鸡也不吃饲料{\r}\NHis chickens won't eat either.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.54,0:35:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如所说，妈妈 布林梅尔先生卖的饲料不佳{\r}\NIt's what you said, Mom. Mr. Brinkmeyer's feed is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.04,0:35:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，凯西 他卖给佛西特先生的是另个牌子{\r}\NNo, Cathy. He sold Mr. Fawcett a different brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.80,0:35:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，你觉得是鸡生病了吗？{\r}\NYou don't think they're getting sick, do you, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.18,0:35:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还是搞不懂 怎么知道我想要爱情鸟{\r}\NI still don't understand how you knew I wanted lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.18,0:35:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哥哥告诉我的{\r}\NYour brother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.06,0:35:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟米契在旧金山认识的？ 没错吧？{\r}\NThen you knew Mitch in San Francisco? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.98,0:35:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不算是{\r}\NNo, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.07,0:35:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契在旧金山认识很多人{\r}\NMitch knows a lot of people in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.07,0:36:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然，他们多半是罪犯{\r}\NOf course, they're mostly hoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.40,0:36:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 凯西！ - 妈，他是最先承认的人{\r}\NCathy! Well, Mom, he's the first to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.99,0:36:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他大半天都待在法院里的拘留室{\r}\NHe spends half his day in the detention cells at the Hall of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.75,0:36:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西，在民主国家 人人都有公平受审的权力{\r}\NIn a democracy, Cathy, everyone is entitled to a fair trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.12,0:36:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哥的工作… - 妈，别说了！{\r}\NYour brother's practice... Oh, Mom, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.96,0:36:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道民主那套狗屁 但他们还是罪犯{\r}\NI know all that democracy jazz. They're still hoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.80,0:36:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他的一位委托人 朝老婆的头开了六枪{\r}\NHe has a client now who shot his wife in the head six times.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.55,0:36:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}六枪！能想像吗？{\r}\NSix times! Can you imagine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开两枪就很夸张了 不觉得吗？{\r}\NI mean, even twice would be overdoing it, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.48,0:36:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他为什么杀她？ - 他当时正在看球赛转播{\r}\NWhy did he shoot her? He was watching a ball game on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.44,0:36:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么？ - 他老婆把电视转台{\r}\NWhat? His wife changed the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 明天会参加我的生日会吗？ - 不会{\r}\NAre you coming to my party tomorrow? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.95,0:36:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我得回旧金山{\r}\NI have to get back to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.49,0:36:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不喜欢我们？ - 亲爱的，我当然喜欢{\r}\NDon't you like us? Oh, darling, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不喜欢博德加湾？ - 我还不知道{\r}\NDon't you like Bodega Bay? I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.96,0:36:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契很喜欢这里 他每个周末都过来{\r}\NMitch likes it very much. He comes up every weekend, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.54,0:37:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}虽然他在市区有间自己的公寓{\r}\Neven though he has his own apartment in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说旧金山就像桥墩上的蚁丘{\r}\NHe says San Francisco's like an anthill at the foot of a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.97,0:37:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}旧金山偶尔是有点忙乱{\r}\NI suppose it does get a little hectic at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}若决定来我的生日会 别说是我告诉的{\r}\NWell, if you do decide to come, don't say I told you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.93,0:37:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这本该是一场惊喜派对{\r}\NIt's supposed to be a surprise party.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们设计了很复杂的计划{\r}\NYou see, they've got this whole complicated thing figured out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.40,0:37:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我下午会去蜜雪儿家玩{\r}\Nwhere I'm going over to Michele's for the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.90,0:37:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但蜜雪儿的妈妈会说她头痛{\r}\Nand Michele's mother will say that she has a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.90,0:37:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是否愿意让她带我回家？{\r}\NWould I mind very much if she took me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.07,0:37:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一到家之后 所有的小孩都会跳出来！{\r}\NThen when I get home here, all the kids will jump out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.99,0:37:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不来吗？ 拜托来嘛？{\r}\NOh, won't you come? Won't you please come?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.96,0:37:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没办法{\r}\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 米契，她很迷人，不是吗？ - 是{\r}\NShe's a charming girl, isn't she, Mitch? Hmm? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非常漂亮{\r}\NCertainly pretty. Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.22,0:37:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你跟她认识多久了？ - 我说过了，我们昨天才认识{\r}\NHow long have you known her? Now, I told you, dear, we met yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.35,0:37:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 在鸟店里 - 在鸟店里{\r}\NIn a bird shop. In a bird shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.60,0:37:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她是鸟店的店员？{\r}\NShe was selling birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.02,0:37:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我只是让她相信 我以为她是店员，然后…{\r}\NNo, no. I just led her into believing that I believed she was, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.90,0:37:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过程很复杂{\r}\NWell, it's all very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.19,0:38:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但她确实买了爱情鸟 还大老远开车过来{\r}\NBut she did buy the lovebirds, and then drove all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.28,0:38:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈 - 怎么？{\r}\N- Mother. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.86,0:38:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上哪间法学院？{\r}\NWhere did you go to law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.74,0:38:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.32,0:38:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是对那样的女孩很好奇{\r}\NI suppose I'm just naturally curious about a girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她很有钱吧？{\r}\NShe's very rich, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.87,0:38:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该是{\r}\NYeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.21,0:38:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她的父亲 是旧金山最大报社的合伙人{\r}\NHer father's part owner of one of the big newspapers in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.54,0:38:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还以为 他能让她的名字不见报{\r}\NYou'd think he could manage to keep her name out of print.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.75,0:38:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她时常登上报纸的八卦专栏{\r}\NShe's always mentioned in the columns, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.92,0:38:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道{\r}\NYes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.76,0:38:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她就是去年在罗马 跳进喷水池的人，对吧？{\r}\NShe is the one who jumped into a fountain in Rome last summer, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.72,0:38:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.72,0:38:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是有点老古板{\r}\NI supposed I'm old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.31,0:38:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道那里的天气很温暖，但…{\r}\NI know it was supposed to be very warm there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上，报纸写说 她当时是一丝不挂{\r}\NWell, actually, the newspapers said she was naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.98,0:38:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道，妈妈{\r}\NYes, I know, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.94,0:38:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这当然不关我的事 但你带这样的女孩…{\r}\NOf course, it's none of my business, but when you bring a girl like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.86,0:38:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈？ - 是？{\r}\NDarling? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.20,0:38:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能自己应付梅兰妮丹尼尔斯{\r}\NI think I can handle Melanie Daniels by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.95,0:38:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要你知道 你要的是什么就好，米契{\r}\NWell, as long as you know what you want, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很清楚我要什么{\r}\NI know exactly what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.21,0:39:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 能自己开车回去？ - 当然{\r}\NBe able to find your way back all right? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.80,0:39:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我能再见吗？ - 旧金山离这里很远{\r}\NWill I be seeing you again? San Francisco's a long way from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一周有五天待在旧金山 而且我时间很多{\r}\NI'm in San Francisco five days a week with a lot of time on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.06,0:39:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想见{\r}\NI'd like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.89,0:39:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以一起去游泳 妈妈告诉我喜欢游泳{\r}\NMaybe we could go swimming or something. Mother tells me you like to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.27,0:39:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 令堂怎么知道我的兴趣？ - 我们都读同一篇八卦专栏{\r}\NHow does Mother know what I like to do? I guess we read the same gossip column.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.15,0:39:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个啊，罗马{\r}\NOh, that. Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.61,0:39:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很喜欢游泳 我们应该处得来{\r}\NYeah, I really like to swim. I think we might get along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以防你有兴趣知道 我是被推进喷水池的{\r}\NIn case you're interested, I was pushed into that fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.95,0:39:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全身赤裸？{\r}\NWithout any clothes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.28,0:39:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我当时衣着整齐 写那篇报导的报社{\r}\NWith all my clothes on. The newspaper that ran that story
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.29,0:39:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}刚好是我父亲的竞争对手{\r}\Nhappens to be a rival of my father's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.00,0:39:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是可怜无辜 被牵连的受害者？{\r}\NYou were just a poor, innocent victim of circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.12,0:39:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不可怜也不无辜{\r}\NI'm neither poor nor innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.96,0:39:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但事实是…{\r}\Nbut the truth of that particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.13,0:39:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实是 跟一群狐群狗党混在一起？{\r}\NThe truth is, you're running around with a pretty wild crowd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.63,0:39:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那倒是真的 但我被推进喷水池{\r}\NYes, that's the truth, but I was pushed into that fountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.55,0:39:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也是事实{\r}\Nand that's the truth, too. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.13,0:39:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的认识安妮海沃斯？{\r}\NDo you really know Annie Hayworth?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我来到这里才认识她{\r}\NNo. At least I didn't until I came up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.81,0:39:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 所以们不是同学？ - 不是{\r}\N- So you didn't go to school together? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.81,0:39:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不是来看她？ - 不是！{\r}\N- And you didn't come up here to see her? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.35,0:40:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 说谎！ - 对，我说谎{\r}\N- You were lying! - Yes, I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.90,0:40:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有写信给我也是骗人的？{\r}\NWhat about the letter you wrote me? Is that a lie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.52,0:40:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的有写{\r}\NNo, I wrote the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 内容是什么？ - 上面写：亲爱的班纳先生{\r}\NWell, what did it say? It said, "Dear Mr. Brenner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.98,0:40:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“我想你需要这对爱情鸟 它们能改善你的人品”{\r}\N"I think you need these lovebirds after all. "They may help your personality."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.74,0:40:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 就这样 - 但撕掉了？{\r}\N- That's what it said. - But you tore it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.91,0:40:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 对 - 为什么？{\r}\N- Yes. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为这似乎太愚蠢了{\r}\NBecause it seemed stupid and foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 跟跳进罗马的喷水池一样 - 我解释过了！{\r}\NLike jumping into a fountain in Rome. I told you what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.71,0:40:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以为我会相信？{\r}\NYou don't expect me to believe that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.87,0:40:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不在乎你信不信！{\r}\NOh, I don't give a damn what you believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我还是想见 - 为什么？{\r}\N- I'd still like to see you. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.54,0:40:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该会很有趣{\r}\NI think it might be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.13,0:40:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那在罗马也许是个好理由 但现在不是了{\r}\NThat might've been good enough in Rome, but it's not good enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我觉得是 - 我不觉得{\r}\N- It is for me. - Well, not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.18,0:40:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要什么？ - 我以为你早知道了{\r}\NWhat do you want? I thought you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.64,0:40:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想要一丝不挂 跳进喷水池里，晚安{\r}\NI want to go through life jumping into fountains naked. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.25,0:41:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 丹尼尔斯小姐，是吗？ - 是{\r}\NMiss Daniels, is that you? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.08,0:41:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗨{\r}\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.38,0:41:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了吗？ 伤口开始痛了？{\r}\NIs something wrong? Is that cut beginning to bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.88,0:41:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，让我烦恼的不是伤口{\r}\NNo, it's not the cut that's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.68,0:41:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要喝点白兰地吗？ - 若有的话，我想喝{\r}\NWould you like some brandy? If you have some, I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.60,0:41:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我去拿 请坐，丹尼尔斯小姐{\r}\NI'll get it. Why don't you sit down, Miss Daniels?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.18,0:41:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想要穿件毛衣或盖件被子吗？{\r}\NOh, would you like a sweater or something, a quilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.31,0:41:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用了，谢谢{\r}\NNo. No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.02,0:41:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 叫我梅兰妮就好 - 没问题{\r}\NWon't you call me Melanie? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.87,0:41:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里的晚上偶尔会有点冷{\r}\NGets a bit chilly here at night sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}尤其是靠近海湾的地方{\r}\Nespecially if you're over near the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.58,0:41:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚过得如何？{\r}\NWell, how did your evening go?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.34,0:41:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}见到莉迪雅了？{\r}\NDid you meet Lydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还是希望我换个话题？{\r}\NOr would you rather I changed the subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.22,0:41:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也好{\r}\NI think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.60,0:42:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 喜欢这个小村庄吗？ - 我恨死了{\r}\NWell, how do you like our little hamlet? I despise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.60,0:42:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里对一般游客没什么魅力{\r}\NWell, I suppose it doesn't offer much to the casual visitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除非对山坡上 一整排的小木屋有兴趣{\r}\Nunless you're thrilled by a collection of shacks on a hillside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.69,0:42:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}得花点时间习惯{\r}\NIt takes a bit of getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.94,0:42:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮，是哪里人？ - 旧金山{\r}\NWhere are you from originally, Annie? San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.95,0:42:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那怎么会来到这里？{\r}\NHow did you happen to come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很久以前 有个朋友邀请我到这里过周末{\r}\NA friend invited me up for a weekend a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.96,0:42:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想也没什么理由好遮掩的{\r}\NLook, I see no reason for being coy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.13,0:42:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个人是米契班纳 应该早就知道了{\r}\NIt was Mitch Brenner. I guess you knew that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.21,0:42:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟我猜的一样{\r}\NI suspected as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.47,0:42:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用担心{\r}\NWell, you needn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.13,0:42:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们老早就分得一干二净{\r}\NIt's been over and done with a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.93,0:42:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮，班纳先生跟我之间 什么都没有{\r}\NAnnie, there's nothing between Mr. Brenner and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.72,0:42:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有吗？{\r}\NIsn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.35,0:42:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许没有吧{\r}\NWell, maybe there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.98,0:42:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许米契跟任何女孩之间 都未曾有过什么{\r}\NMaybe there's never been anything between Mitch and any girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.73,0:42:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么意思？{\r}\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.65,0:42:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也喝点酒好了{\r}\NI think I'll have some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:42:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在旧金山时跟他走得很近{\r}\NI was seeing a lot of him in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.66,0:43:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}某个周末 他邀我和莉迪雅见面{\r}\NThen one weekend, he invited me up to meet Lydia.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.99,0:43:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么时候？{\r}\NWhen was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.53,0:43:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}四年前，他父亲过世后不久{\r}\NOh, four years ago, shortly after his father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.87,0:43:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 当然，现在的情况可能不同了 - 不同？{\r}\NOf course, things may be different now. Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.96,0:43:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莉迪雅啊{\r}\NWith Lydia.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.17,0:43:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她有点冷淡吧？ - 一点点{\r}\NDid she seem a trifle distant? A trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.34,0:43:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那情况可能没什么变{\r}\NWell, then perhaps things aren't quite so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.97,0:43:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她的态度差点害我发疯{\r}\NYou know, her attitude nearly drove me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.52,0:43:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我回到旧金山后 花了好几天想弄清楚 我到底哪里得罪她了{\r}\NWhen I got back to San Francisco, I spent days trying to figure out exactly what I'd done to displease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.65,0:43:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 做了什么？ - 什么都没有{\r}\NWell, what had you done? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.02,0:43:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是出现了，原因呢？ 一个善妒的女人？{\r}\NI simply existed. So what's the answer? A jealous woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.82,0:43:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}占有欲很强的母亲？{\r}\NA clinging, possessive mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.86,0:43:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}错了{\r}\NWrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.32,0:43:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说是恋母情结 我看倒也不是那回事{\r}\NWith all due respect to Oedipus, I don't think that was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.95,0:43:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是什么原因？{\r}\NThen what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.33,0:43:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莉迪雅喜欢我 那才是最奇怪的地方{\r}\NLydia liked me. That's the strange part.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.79,0:43:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在我已不再是威胁 我们竟成了好朋友{\r}\NNow that I'm no longer a threat, we're very good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.13,0:43:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那她当时为何不接受？ - 因为她害怕{\r}\NThen why did she object to you? Because she was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.63,0:44:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}害怕夺走米契？{\r}\NAfraid you'd take Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.43,0:44:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}害怕我对米契的付出{\r}\NAfraid I'd give Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.01,0:44:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不懂{\r}\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.01,0:44:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}害怕任何女人能给米契 莉迪雅唯一能给他的东西，爱{\r}\NAfraid of any woman who would give Mitch the one thing Lydia can give him, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.18,0:44:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就算是 一个善妒和占有欲很强的女人{\r}\NThat adds up to a jealous, possessive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.48,0:44:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不这么想{\r}\NNo, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.94,0:44:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她并不害怕失去米契{\r}\NYou see, she's not afraid of losing Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.86,0:44:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她只害怕被抛弃{\r}\NShe's only afraid of being abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.57,0:44:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}某人得告诉她 她也会因此多一个女儿{\r}\NSomeone ought to tell her she'd be gaining a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.07,0:44:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，她已经有个女儿了{\r}\NNo. She already has a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.08,0:44:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那米契呢？ 他都没有表示意见？{\r}\NWell, what about Mitch? Didn't he have anything to say about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.17,0:44:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能理解他的立场{\r}\NWell, I can understand his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.84,0:44:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他父亲死后 他跟莉迪雅过得很辛苦{\r}\NHe'd just been through a lot with Lydia after his father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.71,0:44:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他可不想再重来一次{\r}\NHe didn't want to risk going through it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我懂了{\r}\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.13,0:44:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以我们分手了 当然不是立刻{\r}\NSo it ended. Not right then, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.72,0:44:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们回到旧金山后 偶尔还是会见面{\r}\NWe went back to San Francisco, saw each other now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.14,0:44:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我们都知道这结束了{\r}\Nbut we both knew it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.72,0:44:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那为何搬到博德加湾？{\r}\NThen what are you doing here in Bodega Bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.81,0:44:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想留在米契身边{\r}\NI wanted to be near Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.27,0:44:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道我们分手了，但是…{\r}\NOh, it was over and done with, and I knew it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.02,0:45:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我仍想留在他身边{\r}\NI still wanted to be near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.74,0:45:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还是很喜欢他{\r}\NYou see, I still like him a hell of a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.20,0:45:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想失去这段友情{\r}\Nand I don't want to lose that friendship, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.88,0:45:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喂{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.05,0:45:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.88,0:45:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我还没睡{\r}\NNo, no, no, I wasn't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.09,0:45:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，不久之前{\r}\NYes, just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.26,0:45:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然，稍等{\r}\NSure. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.43,0:45:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契打来的{\r}\NIt's Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.60,0:45:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他要找{\r}\NFor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.23,0:45:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喂？ 对，我是梅兰妮{\r}\NHello? Oh, yes, this is Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.95,0:45:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好，谢谢{\r}\NFine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.12,0:45:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一点都不难 我只是沿着马路开{\r}\NNo, no trouble at all. I simply followed the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.66,0:45:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没必要道歉{\r}\NWell... there's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.83,0:45:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能理解{\r}\NI can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.34,0:46:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你人真好，不，我没生气{\r}\NThat's very kind of you. No, I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.05,0:46:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没办法，我得回旧金山{\r}\NWell, I couldn't. I have to get back to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.72,0:46:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想让凯西失望，不过…{\r}\NNo, I wouldn't want to disappoint Cathy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.23,0:46:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了{\r}\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.19,0:46:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，我会到场{\r}\NAll right. Yes, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.78,0:46:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安，米契{\r}\NGood night, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.37,0:46:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他要我明天下午 参加凯西的生日会{\r}\NHe wants me to go to Cathy's party tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.83,0:46:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我答应了{\r}\NI said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.04,0:46:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一定会很好玩{\r}\NIt should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.87,0:46:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也会去帮忙{\r}\NI'll be there, too, to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.00,0:46:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这真是没必要{\r}\NOh, it seems so pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.01,0:46:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要去睡觉了 今天真是漫长{\r}\NWell, I think I'll go to sleep. It's been a busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.22,0:46:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的行李{\r}\NMy luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.73,0:47:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真漂亮，在哪买的？ 布林梅尔的店？{\r}\NThat's pretty. Where'd you get that? Brinkmeyer's? Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.90,0:47:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}认为我该参加吗？{\r}\NDo you think I should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.07,0:47:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这要由决定{\r}\NWell, that's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.49,0:47:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，这得由莉迪雅决定吧？{\r}\NNo, it's really up to Lydia, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.16,0:47:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别管莉迪雅了，想去吗？{\r}\NNever mind Lydia. Do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.16,0:47:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.04,0:47:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那就去吧 - 谢谢，安妮{\r}\NThen go. Thank you, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.79,0:47:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}会是谁啊{\r}\NWonder who that can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.76,0:47:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有人吗？{\r}\NIs someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.92,0:47:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是谁？ - 看{\r}\NWho is it? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.22,0:47:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真可怜，可能是天色太暗迷路了{\r}\NPoor thing. Probably lost his way in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.85,0:47:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但天色不暗，安妮{\r}\NBut it isn't dark, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.60,0:47:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚是满月{\r}\NThere's a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.45,0:47:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西，非常好{\r}\NCathy, that's very good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.62,0:47:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开始吧{\r}\NOkay. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.56,0:48:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做得好，别让他抓到了{\r}\NAttagirl. Come on. Don't let him get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.45,0:48:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不能再喝了，我还要开车{\r}\NNo, I really shouldn't have any more. I'm driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.50,0:48:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上，我想请留下来吃晚饭{\r}\NWell, actually, I'm trying to get you to stay for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.67,0:48:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还剩下很多烤牛肉{\r}\NA lot of roast beef left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.17,0:48:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不行，我得回家了 - 好吧{\r}\NNo, I couldn't possibly. I have to get back. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.21,0:48:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 干杯 - 干杯{\r}\N- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.51,0:48:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到底为什么要急着走？ 旧金山有要紧的事吗？{\r}\NSeriously, why do you have to rush off? What's so important in San Francisco?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.14,0:49:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明天早上还得工作{\r}\NWell, I have to get to work tomorrow morning, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.77,0:49:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有工作？ - 我有很多工作{\r}\NYou have a job? I have several jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.85,0:49:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么工作？ - 我有各式各样的工作{\r}\NWhat do you do? I do different things on different days.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.31,0:49:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比如说？{\r}\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.32,0:49:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我周一和周三 在机场的旅客服务柜台工作{\r}\NWell, on Mondays and Wednesdays, I work for the Travelers' Aid at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.19,0:49:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}协助旅客？{\r}\NHelping travelers?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.24,0:49:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，是去误导他们 我以为你了解我的个性{\r}\NNo, misdirecting them. I thought you could read my character.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.03,0:49:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}周二我在柏克莱大学 修读普通语义学的课程{\r}\NOn Tuesdays, I take a course in General Semantics at Berkeley,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.66,0:49:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寻找新的脏话{\r}\Nfinding new four-letter words.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.83,0:49:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那不算工作… - 是说不必…{\r}\N- That's not a job, of course... - You mean, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.13,0:49:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}周四我要开会和出席午餐会{\r}\NAnd on Thursdays, I have my meeting and lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.92,0:49:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我猜是在地狱吧{\r}\NIn the underworld, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.71,0:49:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恐怕要让你失望了{\r}\NI shall disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.92,0:49:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要帮助 一个韩国小男孩去上学{\r}\NWe're sending a little Korean boy through school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.05,0:49:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们正在为此募款{\r}\NWe actually raise money for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.10,0:49:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗马的事…{\r}\NYou see, Rome...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.52,0:49:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一整个夏天，我只顾着…{\r}\NThat entire summer, I did nothing but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.07,0:49:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗马很容易让人迷失{\r}\NWell, it was very easy to get lost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.11,0:49:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回国之后，我认为我该开始…{\r}\NSo when I came back, I thought it was time I began...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.78,0:49:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}重新寻找某些东西{\r}\NOh, I don't know, finding something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.95,0:50:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以周一到周四 我让自己保持忙碌{\r}\NSo, on Mondays and Thursdays, I keep myself busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.46,0:50:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那周五呢？ - 周五？ 没事{\r}\NWhat about Fridays? Fridays? They're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.80,0:50:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我偶尔会在周五到鸟店逛逛{\r}\NI sometimes go to bird shops on Fridays.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.72,0:50:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很高兴会去{\r}\NI'm very glad you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.51,0:50:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美好天真的一天{\r}\NA nice, innocent, little day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.85,0:50:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然{\r}\NOh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.81,0:50:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有个泰莎姑妈 你有姑妈吗？{\r}\NI have an Aunt Tessa. Have you got an Aunt Tessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.27,0:50:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的姑妈拘谨又古板{\r}\NMine is very prim and straight-laced.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.27,0:50:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等她从欧洲回来后 我要送她一只八哥鸟{\r}\NI'm giving her a mynah bird when she comes back from Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.28,0:50:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}八哥鸟会说话 如果这只鸟会说几个{\r}\NMynah birds talk, you know. Can you see my Aunt Tessa's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.32,0:50:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在柏克莱学到的词 你能想像泰莎姑妈的表情吗？{\r}\Nwhen this one tells us one or two of the words I've picked up at Berkeley?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.70,0:50:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}需要一点母亲的关爱，孩子{\r}\NYou need a mother's care, my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不需要我母亲的爱 - 很抱歉{\r}\NNot my mother's. Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.01,0:50:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有什么好抱歉的？{\r}\NWhat have you got to be sorry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.18,0:51:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的母亲？ 别浪费时间了{\r}\NMy mother? Don't waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.97,0:51:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我11岁时，她抛弃我们 跟一个东部的饭店员工跑了{\r}\NShe ditched us when I was 11 and ran off with some hotel man in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.39,0:51:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道什么是母爱？{\r}\NYou know what a mother's love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.81,0:51:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我知道 - 你是指被抛弃比较好？{\r}\NYes, I do. You mean it's better to be ditched?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.15,0:51:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，有母亲的爱比较好 再也没见过她了？{\r}\NNo. I think it's better to be loved. Don't you ever see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.66,0:51:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道她在哪里{\r}\NI don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.00,0:51:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还是去找孩子们玩吧{\r}\NWell, maybe I ought to go join the other children.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.68,0:51:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开始吧，一…{\r}\NAll right. Here we go. One...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.85,0:51:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二…{\r}\NTwo...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.56,0:51:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}三…{\r}\NThree...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.14,0:51:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧{\r}\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.20,0:52:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们看！{\r}\NLook! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.03,0:52:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿！不准碰我！{\r}\NHey! No touching allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.23,0:52:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}帮我把孩子们带进屋里{\r}\NHelp me get the children into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.77,0:53:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进去吧{\r}\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.28,0:53:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，它们离开了吗？{\r}\NHave they gone, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.95,0:53:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 离开了 - 有人受伤吗？{\r}\NI think so. Is anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.41,0:53:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}珍妮的脸颊被抓伤，但无大碍{\r}\NJenny got a scratch down her cheek, but it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.24,0:53:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是第三次了{\r}\NThat makes three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.21,0:53:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，这很不寻常吧？{\r}\NMitch, this isn't usual, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.79,0:53:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}昨天在船上攻击我的海鸥 昨晚在安妮家也有一只，现在…{\r}\NThe gull when I was in the boat yesterday, the one at Annie's last night, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}昨晚？ 什么意思？{\r}\NLast night? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.46,0:53:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有只海鸥撞上安妮家的大门 米契，怎么回事？{\r}\NA gull smashed into Annie's front door. Mitch, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.97,0:53:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道，得回安妮家吗？{\r}\NI don't know. Do you have to go back to Annie's?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.26,0:53:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我的行李都在车上{\r}\NNo. I have my things in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.85,0:53:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在回去之前 留下来吃点东西吧，我会安心点{\r}\NStay and have something to eat before you start back. I'd feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.66,0:54:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要加芥末吗？ - 不用，谢谢{\r}\NWould you like some mustard with that? No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.95,0:54:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮为何不留下来？{\r}\NWhy didn't Annie stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.33,0:54:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她说她要回家 接她妹妹从东部打来的电话{\r}\NSaid something about going home to take a call from her sister in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.29,0:54:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们怎么了？{\r}\NWhat's the matter with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.33,0:54:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这些鸟是怎么了？ - 咖啡要放在哪里？{\r}\NWhat's the matter with all the birds? Where did you want this coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.67,0:54:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 放在桌上，亲爱的 - 你动作快一点，米契{\r}\NHere on the table, honey. Hurry up with yours, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.84,0:54:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐一定很想上路了{\r}\NI'm sure Miss Daniels wants to be on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.63,0:54:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚该留下来，梅兰妮{\r}\NI think you ought to stay the night, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.14,0:54:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}楼上有一间多出来的房间{\r}\NWe have an extra room upstairs and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.18,0:54:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚上的路况也很糟糕{\r}\NThat road can be a pretty bad one at night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.81,0:54:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}若我开到圣塔罗沙{\r}\NIf I go across to Santa Rosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.10,0:54:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就能早一点上高速公路 不是吗？{\r}\NI'll come out on the freeway much earlier, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.52,0:54:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，走高速公路快多了{\r}\NYes, and the freeway is much quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.52,0:54:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但她会碰上 返回旧金山的大量车潮{\r}\NBut she'll be hitting all the heavy traffic going back to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.90,0:54:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那对爱情鸟叫得好厉害{\r}\NJust listen to those lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.36,0:54:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契{\r}\NMitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.00,0:55:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}遮住脸和眼睛！{\r}\NCover your faces! Cover your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.04,0:56:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是麻雀{\r}\NThat's a sparrow, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.29,0:56:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们知道，艾尔 - 你们当时有点灯吗？{\r}\NWe know what it is, Al. Did you have a light burning or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.96,0:56:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有，但灯光 不至于会从烟囱传出去{\r}\NYes, but there wouldn't have been that much light going up the chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.09,0:56:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟有时会被灯光吸引 但这情况确实少见{\r}\N'Cause sometimes birds are attracted by light, you know. Sure is a peculiar thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.01,0:56:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我们得想个办法解决！{\r}\NWell, all right, but we've got to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.68,0:56:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不懂你的意思，米契 解决什么？{\r}\NI don't think I get you, Mitch. Do about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.15,0:56:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟入侵房子{\r}\NWell, the birds invaded the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.44,0:56:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该是它们进到屋里后 惊慌失措了，如此而已{\r}\NWhat's more likely, they got in the room and was just panicked. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.44,0:56:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道鸟在密闭的空间里会惊慌{\r}\NAll right, I'll admit a bird will panic in an enclosed room,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.65,0:56:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但它们不是不小心飞进来 而是从烟囱飞下来的{\r}\Nbut they didn't just get in. They came in, right down the chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.57,0:56:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我老婆曾在她的汽车后座上 发现一只鸟{\r}\NMy wife found a bird in the back seat of her car once.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.20,0:56:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟他说生日会上的事{\r}\NTell him about the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.79,0:57:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错，今天下午 我们在家举办凯西的生日会{\r}\NThat's right. We had a party here this afternoon for Cathy, for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.71,0:57:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她几岁了？ - 11岁！生日会开到一半{\r}\NHow old is she? Eleven! In the middle of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.33,0:57:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几只海鸥冲向孩子们！{\r}\Nsome seagulls came down at the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.00,0:57:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐 昨天才被一只海鸥攻击{\r}\NMiss Daniels was attacked by a gull only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.55,0:57:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，孩子们打扰那些鸟了吗？{\r}\NYeah. Were the kids bothering the birds or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.05,0:57:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为你要是在它们周围捣乱{\r}\N'Cause if you make any kind of a disturbance near them,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.18,0:57:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们就会追你{\r}\Nthey'll just come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.30,0:57:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾尔，孩子们当时在玩游戏 海鸥就攻击了{\r}\NAl, the children were playing a game. Those gulls attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.52,0:57:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莉迪雅，不觉得 用 “攻击” 太严重了吗？{\r}\NNow, Lydia, "attack" is a pretty strong word, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.02,0:57:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海鸥不会无故攻击人类{\r}\NI mean, birds just don't go around attacking people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.40,0:57:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}懂我的意思吗？{\r}\Nwithout no reason. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.36,0:57:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大概是孩子吓到它们了{\r}\NThe kids probably scared them, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.23,0:57:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些鸟攻击我们{\r}\NThese birds attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.07,0:57:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我承认这屋子是被搞得一团乱{\r}\NYou got quite a mess here, I'll admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.87,0:57:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你也许该在烟囱口加片纱网{\r}\NMaybe you ought to put some screen on top of your chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.62,0:57:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 需要人手帮忙清理吗？ - 不用了{\r}\NYou want some help cleaning up? No. I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.91,0:57:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}清理起来应该不难{\r}\NIt shouldn't be too much of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.00,0:57:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我带凯西去睡觉{\r}\NI'll take Cathy up to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.30,0:57:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我该留下，你觉得呢？{\r}\NI think I should stay, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.76,0:57:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那再好不过了{\r}\NIt would be nice if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.09,0:57:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的行李在车上{\r}\NMy things are in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.30,0:57:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 跟我来吧？ - 好{\r}\N- Do you want to go with me? - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.85,0:58:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 米契，还需要我帮忙吗？ - 不，谢了，艾尔{\r}\NWell, anything else I can do, Mitch? No, thanks, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.35,0:58:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们没问题的 - 晚安，莉迪雅{\r}\NWe'll be all right. Good night, Lydia.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.02,0:58:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}确实很奇怪{\r}\NSure is peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.24,0:58:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契！{\r}\NMitch. Mitch. Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.41,0:58:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈，什么事？ - 我送凯西去上学{\r}\NYes, Mother? I'm going to drop Cathy off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.79,0:58:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也许会去佛西特农场看看{\r}\NI'll probably drive over to the Fawcett farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.71,0:58:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.54,0:59:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安{\r}\NMorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.46,0:59:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安，乔治 佛西特先生在吗？{\r}\NGood morning, George. Is Mr. Fawcett around?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.01,0:59:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在，女士{\r}\NI think so, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.51,0:59:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今早还没看到他 但他应该在家里{\r}\NAin't seen him this morning, but he ought to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.68,0:59:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢了{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.79,0:59:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹，你在家吗？{\r}\NDan, are you home?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.77,1:01:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈！{\r}\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.11,1:01:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了？ 怎么回事？{\r}\NWhat is it, dear? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.41,1:01:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾尔马龙副警长刚来过电话 他要我过去佛西特家{\r}\NAl Malone, the deputy, just called. He wants me over at the Fawcett place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣塔罗沙的警探会赶到那里{\r}\NSome detectives from Santa Rosa will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.29,1:01:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没问题吧？ - 是{\r}\N- Will it be all right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.71,1:02:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是要替母亲泡点茶{\r}\NI was just taking your mother in some tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.63,1:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请小心点{\r}\NOh, be careful, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.19,1:02:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也小心点{\r}\NAnd you be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.51,1:02:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契？{\r}\NMitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.06,1:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我，班纳太太{\r}\NNo, it's me, Mrs. Brenner.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.77,1:03:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我认为会想喝点茶 - 谢谢{\r}\NI thought you might like some tea. Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.98,1:03:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契在哪里？{\r}\NWhere's Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.32,1:03:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾尔马龙要他去佛西特农场一趟{\r}\NAl Malone wanted him out at the Fawcett farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.74,1:03:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么？ 艾尔不相信我的说词？{\r}\NWhy? Didn't Al believe my story?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.66,1:03:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他从农场打电话过来的{\r}\NHe was calling from the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.53,1:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他看见了 - 一定是{\r}\NThen he saw. Oh, he must have.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.37,1:03:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们找来圣塔罗沙警方{\r}\NThey sent for the Santa Rosa police.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.71,1:03:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那又能怎样？{\r}\NWhat good will they do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.25,1:03:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西在学校没问题吧？{\r}\NDo you think Cathy's all right at the school?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.59,1:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我确定她很安全{\r}\NYes, I'm sure she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.18,1:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}觉得我很可笑吗？{\r}\NDo I sound very foolish to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.89,1:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不{\r}\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.89,1:03:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直看见丹的脸{\r}\NI keep seeing Dan's face.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.27,1:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}学校里有很大的窗户{\r}\NAnd they have such big windows at the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.69,1:03:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹房间里的窗户全破了{\r}\NAll the windows are broken in Dan's bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.82,1:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 全部的窗户！ - 别再想那些了{\r}\NAll the windows! Try not to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.07,1:03:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真希望我能坚强一点{\r}\NI wish I were a stronger person.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.41,1:04:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}四年前，我失去丈夫{\r}\NI lost my husband four years ago, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.42,1:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这糟透了 依赖别人给力量{\r}\NIt's terrible how you depend on someone else for strength, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.92,1:04:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但这力量突然间没了 独留一人{\r}\Nsuddenly all the strength is gone, and you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.60,1:04:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望偶尔也能放松{\r}\NI'd love to be able to relax sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.27,1:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望能睡得着{\r}\NI'd love to be able to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.44,1:04:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 凯西不会出事吧？ - 有安妮在{\r}\NDo you think Cathy's all right? Annie's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.94,1:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她没事的{\r}\NShe'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.37,1:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我通常不会这样{\r}\NI'm not like this, you know? Not usually.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.79,1:04:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不会处处担心我的孩子{\r}\NI don't fuss and fret about my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.88,1:04:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}法兰克去世后…{\r}\NWhen Frank died...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.21,1:04:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他生前很了解孩子们 非常了解他们{\r}\NYou see, he understood the children. He really understood them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.38,1:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他就是有办法进到他们的世界 成为他们的朋友{\r}\NHe had the knack of entering into their world and becoming part of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.68,1:05:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是很厉害的本事 - 是{\r}\NThat's a very rare talent. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.31,1:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真希望能像他一样{\r}\NOh, I wish, I wish, I wish I could be like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.90,1:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我好想他{\r}\NI miss him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.20,1:05:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}即使到了现在 我偶尔早上醒来还会想着{\r}\NSometimes, even now, I wake up in the morning and I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.33,1:05:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“我得替法兰克煮早餐”{\r}\N"I must get Frank's breakfast."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.66,1:05:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}接着我起身 这是让人起床的大好理由{\r}\NAnd I get up, and there's a very good reason for getting out of bed,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.42,1:05:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到{\r}\Nuntil, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.54,1:05:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我记起来{\r}\NI remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.05,1:05:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想念跟他聊天{\r}\NI miss talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.18,1:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西还是个孩子，而米契…{\r}\NCathy's a child, of course, and Mitch...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.85,1:05:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契有自己的生活{\r}\NWell, Mitch has his own life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.11,1:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很高兴他今天留下来{\r}\NI'm glad he stayed here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.65,1:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有他在我安心多了{\r}\NI feel safer with him here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.11,1:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 想休息了吗？ - 不{\r}\NWould you like to rest now? No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.03,1:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，别走{\r}\NNo, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.20,1:06:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我觉得我一点都不了解{\r}\NI feel as if I don't understand you at all,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.66,1:06:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想好好认识{\r}\Nand I want so much to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.54,1:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么？{\r}\NWhy, Mrs. Brenner?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.55,1:06:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我儿子似乎很喜欢{\r}\NBecause my son seems to be very fond of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.47,1:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而我不知道我做何感想{\r}\Nand I don't quite know how I feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.60,1:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我甚至不知道我喜不喜欢{\r}\NI don't even know if I like you or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.39,1:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喜欢我有那么重要吗？{\r}\NIs that so important, your liking me?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.27,1:06:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是这么想的{\r}\NWell, yes. I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.48,1:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契对我来说很重要{\r}\NMitch is important to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.11,1:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想喜欢他选上的女孩{\r}\NI want to like whatever girl he chooses.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.66,1:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果不喜欢呢？{\r}\NAnd perhaps if you don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.83,1:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么除了我以外 对任何人来说都无所谓{\r}\NWell, then I don't think it'll matter very much to anyone but me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.04,1:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想米契也会在意的{\r}\NOh, I think it would also matter to Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.21,1:06:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契总是照自己的意思行事{\r}\NMitch has always done exactly what he wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.05,1:07:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是我不想被抛弃{\r}\NBut, you see, I don't want to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.89,1:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我无法忍受被抛弃！{\r}\NI don't think I could bear to be left alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.77,1:07:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原谅我{\r}\NOh, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.65,1:07:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原谅我{\r}\NOh, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.86,1:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟杀人的事让我好心烦{\r}\NThis business with the birds has upset me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.53,1:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果米契不在 我真不知道该怎么办{\r}\NI don't know what I'd do if Mitch weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.99,1:07:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班纳太太，何不试着睡一下？{\r}\NWhy don't you try to sleep now, Mrs. Brenner?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.33,1:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望我能坚强点{\r}\NI wish I was stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.62,1:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}觉得她会没事吗？{\r}\NDo you think she's all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.46,1:07:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她在学校里不会有事吧？{\r}\NDo you think she's all right at the school?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.88,1:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要我去接她吗？ - 我不能这样要求{\r}\NWould you like me to go for her? Oh, I couldn't ask it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.55,1:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不介意，真的 - 是吗？{\r}\NOh, I don't mind, really. Would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.89,1:07:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我感觉好多了 - 我现在就去{\r}\NI'd feel so much better. I'll go right now.
