Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.01,1:11:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了，孩子们 请把歌本收起来{\r}\NAll right, children. Now, please put your song books away,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.18,1:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}站在你们的桌子边{\r}\Nthen stand up alongside your desks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.18,1:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等大家准备好 我们就到外面去玩{\r}\NWe'll go out for recess as soon as everybody gets ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.68,1:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等大家安静下来{\r}\NWe are not going into the playground
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.52,1:12:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们才要去游乐场{\r}\Nuntil everybody has quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.99,1:12:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 快点把门关上 - 什么？{\r}\N- Close that door. Quickly. Please. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.66,1:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 怎么了？ - 看{\r}\N- What is it? - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.96,1:12:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们得把孩子们带离学校{\r}\NWe've got to get the children out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.42,1:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了，孩子们，安静{\r}\NAll right, children. Now, quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.01,1:12:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐想看看{\r}\NQuiet. Miss Daniels would like to see
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.05,1:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们进行防火演习的样子{\r}\Nhow we conduct ourselves during a fire drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.14,1:12:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请你们让她见识一下 你们有多安静、多听话{\r}\NI would like you to show her how quiet and obedient you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.23,1:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们现在要离开学校了 - 离开学校？{\r}\NOh, we're going out of school now. Leave school?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.94,1:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}住在附近的人 我们要你们直接回家{\r}\NWe want those of you who live nearby to go directly home.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.98,1:12:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回家？{\r}\NHome?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.40,1:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}其他的人则一路跑到 山下的旅馆，听清楚了吗？{\r}\NI want the rest of you to go down the hill all the way to the hotel. Now, is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.74,1:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，海沃斯老师{\r}\NYes, Miss Hayworth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.78,1:12:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅兰妮？{\r}\NMelanie?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.95,1:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要大家安静地离开{\r}\NI want you to go as quietly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.58,1:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我要你们跑之前 不准出声音{\r}\NDo not make a sound until I tell you to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.21,1:13:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跑得越快越好 大家都听懂了？{\r}\NThen run as quickly as you can. Now, does everybody understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.05,1:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}懂了，海沃斯老师{\r}\NYes, Miss Hayworth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.05,1:13:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}约翰，由你带头{\r}\NAll right, John, you lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.81,1:14:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西！{\r}\NCathy! Cathy!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.25,1:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爸爸，有好几百只鸟{\r}\NWell, Daddy, there were hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.13,1:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有歇斯底里{\r}\NNo, I'm not hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.42,1:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我试着尽可能冷静地向你解释{\r}\NI'm trying to tell you this as calmly as I know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.80,1:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，是，爸爸{\r}\NAll right, Daddy. Yes, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.51,1:16:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是刚才，不是15分钟前{\r}\NWell, just now. Not 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.14,1:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在学校{\r}\NAt the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.48,1:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我没有，等等 学校叫什么名字？{\r}\NNo, I don't. Just a minute. What's the name of the school?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.10,1:16:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 博德加湾学校 - 博德加湾学校{\r}\NJust the Bodega Bay School. The Bodega Bay School.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.82,1:16:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道有多少学生 30或40个吧{\r}\NWell, I don't know how many children, 30 or 40.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.91,1:16:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，学生出了学校 鸟才开始攻击{\r}\NNo, the birds didn't attack until the children were outside the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.12,1:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 邦迪太太，需要什么？ - 我要换零钱，卡特先生{\r}\NHelp you, Mrs. Bundy? I need some change, Mr. Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.66,1:16:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该是乌鸦{\r}\NCrows, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.16,1:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道{\r}\NWell, I don't know, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.37,1:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乌鸦跟黑鸟有什么差别吗？{\r}\NIs there a difference between crows and blackbirds?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.71,1:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 差别可大了，小姐 - 谢谢{\r}\NThere is very definitely a difference, miss. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.30,1:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们是不同的鸟，爸爸{\r}\NThey're different, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.51,1:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为这些是乌鸦{\r}\NWell, I think these were crows.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.93,1:16:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，好几百只{\r}\NWell, yes. Hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.30,1:16:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们攻击孩子，攻击他们！{\r}\NYes, they attacked the children. Attacked them!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.10,1:16:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道何时 但我现在走不开，爸爸{\r}\NWell, I don't know when, but I simply can't leave now, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.94,1:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，再见{\r}\NAll right. Yes. Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.27,1:17:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们都属雀形目，但品种不同{\r}\NThey're both perching birds, of course, but quite different species.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.15,1:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乌鸦的学名为短嘴鸦{\r}\NThe crow is Corvus brachyrhynchos,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.74,1:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黑鸟的学名则是蓝头黑鹂{\r}\Nand the blackbird is Euphagus cyanocephalus.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.20,1:17:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.20,1:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你有佛西特农场的电话吗？ - 这本册子上有{\r}\NYou have the number at the Fawcett farm? Right here in this book, miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.87,1:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邦迪太太 我认为是乌鸦或是黑鸟{\r}\NI can't see that it makes any difference, Mrs. Bundy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.38,1:17:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}都没有差别{\r}\NCrows or blackbirds,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.59,1:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果它们攻击学生 那事态就严重了{\r}\Nif the school was attacked, that's pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.09,1:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为这两种鸟{\r}\NI hardly think that either species
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.09,1:17:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}都没有足够的智慧 能发动一场集体攻击{\r}\Nwould have sufficient intelligence to launch a massed attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.34,1:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们的头颅太小…{\r}\NTheir brainpans are not big enough to...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.85,1:17:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我刚从学校过来，女士{\r}\NI just came from the school, madam.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.60,1:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我对它们的头颅一无所知，但…{\r}\NI don't know anything about their brainpans, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.06,1:17:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我知道{\r}\NWell, I do. I do know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.65,1:17:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我正好对鸟类学有兴趣{\r}\NOrnithology happens to be my avocation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.23,1:17:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟类不是凶猛的生物{\r}\NBirds are not aggressive creatures, miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.57,1:17:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们为这世界增色 反而是人类…{\r}\NThey bring beauty into the world. It is mankind, rather, who...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.65,1:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}山姆！三份南方炸鸡{\r}\NSam! Three southern fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.74,1:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全搭配烤马铃薯{\r}\NBaked potato on all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.74,1:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请找米契班纳{\r}\NYes, may I speak to Mitch Brenner, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.29,1:17:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，我等{\r}\NYes, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.70,1:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}反而是人类坚持要{\r}\NIt is mankind, rather, who insists upon
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.75,1:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让生物难以活在地球上{\r}\Nmaking it difficult for life to exist upon this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.46,1:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 如果没有鸟类… - 邦迪太太，不明白{\r}\NNow, if it were not for the birds... Mrs. Bundy, you don't seem to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.80,1:18:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这位小姐说学生被鸟攻击了{\r}\NThis young lady said there was an attack on the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.09,1:18:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不可能！ - 米契？{\r}\N- Impossible! - Oh, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.09,1:18:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好险我找到你了{\r}\NOh, I'm glad I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.26,1:18:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 可怕的事… - 世界末日到了！{\r}\NSomething terrible has... It's the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.35,1:18:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两杯血腥玛丽，迪克{\r}\NTwo Bloody Marys, Deke.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.31,1:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}学校出了什么事？{\r}\NWhat actually happened at the school?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.81,1:18:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一群乌鸦攻击学生{\r}\NBunch of crows attacked the school kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.60,1:18:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}世界末日到了 因此主耶和华{\r}\NIt's the end of the world. "Thus saith the Lord God
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.19,1:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对高山、丘陵、河流和山谷{\r}\N"unto the mountains and the hills, "and the rivers and the valleys.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.82,1:18:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说道{\r}\N"Behold I, even I,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.57,1:18:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必让你们遭遇刀害{\r}\N"shall bring a sword upon you,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.57,1:18:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“我必摧毁你们的邱坛”{\r}\N"and I will devastate your high places."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.49,1:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以西结书第六章{\r}\NEzekiel, chapter six.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.50,1:18:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}灾祸降临于清早起床{\r}\N"Woe unto them that rise up early in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.92,1:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“就追求烈酒之人”{\r}\N"that they may follow strong drink."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.54,1:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以赛亚书第五章 世界末日到了{\r}\NIsaiah, chapter five. It's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.50,1:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不认为 几只鸟会造成世界末日{\r}\NI hardly think a few birds are going to bring about the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.55,1:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这不是几只鸟而已 - 我不知道博德加湾{\r}\NThese weren't a few birds. I didn't know there were many crows in Bodega Bay
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.84,1:18:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这个时节会有这么多乌鸦{\r}\Nthis time of year.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.85,1:18:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乌鸦会固定留在它的栖息地里{\r}\NThe crow is a permanent resident throughout its range.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.48,1:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上，在圣诞节期间 我们计算过有…{\r}\NIn fact, during our Christmas count, we recorded...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.98,1:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邦迪太太 你们算过有多少只海鸥？{\r}\NHow many gulls did you count, Mrs. Bundy?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.31,1:19:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}休尔斯先生，哪种海鸥？ 海鸥有分很多种{\r}\NWhich gulls, Mr. Sholes? There are several varieties.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.57,1:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}危害我渔船的那种{\r}\NThe ones who've been playing devil with my fishing boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.82,1:19:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 海鸥也给你带来麻烦？ - 上周攻击我的一艘船{\r}\NHave you had trouble with gulls? One of my boats did, last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.82,1:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这位小姐周六才被海鸥攻击{\r}\NThis young lady was hit by a gull only Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.66,1:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迪克，我还在等血腥玛丽{\r}\NDeke, I'm still waiting for those Bloody Marys.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.83,1:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马上来{\r}\NComing right up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.16,1:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}能否请他们小声点？{\r}\NCould you ask them to lower their voices, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.21,1:19:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们吓到孩子了{\r}\NThey're frightening the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.63,1:19:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一大群海鸥几乎弄翻了我的船{\r}\NA whole flock of gulls nearly capsized one of my boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.38,1:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}差点扯下船长的手臂{\r}\NPractically tore the skipper's arm off.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.38,1:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你吓到孩子了，小声点 - 好{\r}\NYou're scaring the kids. Keep it low. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.05,1:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他也吓到我了{\r}\NYeah, well, he's scaring me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.97,1:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的意思是这些…{\r}\NAre you trying to say that all these...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.39,1:19:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，这不可能，赛巴斯汀{\r}\NNah, that sounds impossible, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.39,1:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迪克，我只是说出 我的船遇到什么事{\r}\NDeke, look, I'm just telling you what happened to one of my boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.06,1:19:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海鸥想要你船上的鱼，休尔斯先生{\r}\NThe gulls were after your fish, Mr. Sholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.90,1:19:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请你用点逻辑{\r}\NReally, let's be logical about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.36,1:19:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那攻击学生的乌鸦呢？{\r}\NWhat were the crows after at the school?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.57,1:19:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}认为它们想要什么？ 是…{\r}\NWhat do you think they were after? Miss...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.86,1:19:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯 我想它们要的是孩子们{\r}\NDaniels. I think they were after the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.74,1:19:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}目的呢？{\r}\NFor what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.08,1:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 杀了他们 - 为什么？{\r}\NTo kill them. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.58,1:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道原因{\r}\NI don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.42,1:20:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不这么认为{\r}\NI thought not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.84,1:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹尼尔斯小姐，自始祖鸟开始{\r}\NBirds have been on this planet, Miss Daniels,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.88,1:20:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟类在一亿四千万年前 就出现在地球上{\r}\Nsince Archaeopteryx, 140 million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.68,1:20:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们等了那么久 才跟人类宣战{\r}\NDoesn't it seem odd that they'd wait all that time
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.80,1:20:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是有点奇怪吗？{\r}\Nto start a war against humanity?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.56,1:20:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没人说这是战争 - 威士忌加水{\r}\NNo one called it a war. Scotch, light on the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.02,1:20:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟休尔斯先生 似乎就是这个意思{\r}\NYou and Mr. Sholes seem to be implying as much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.98,1:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁说到战争了？ 我只是说有海鸥…{\r}\NWho said anything about a war? All I said, some gulls...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.81,1:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再来点咖啡？ - 不了{\r}\N- Want some more coffee? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.82,1:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}…攻击我的船{\r}\N...came down on one of my boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.82,1:20:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如所说的 它们要的可能是鱼{\r}\NThey could have been after the fish, just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.11,1:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}船长应该要射死它们{\r}\N- The Captain should have shot at them. - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.99,1:20:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海鸥是食腐动物 多数的鸟类都是{\r}\NGulls are scavengers, anyway. Most birds are.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.58,1:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拿起枪 让它们在地球上消失吧！{\r}\NGet yourselves guns and wipe them off the face of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.25,1:20:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是不可能的 - 为什么？{\r}\NThat would hardly be possible. Why not, Mrs. Bundy?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.96,1:20:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为当今世界上{\r}\NBecause there are 8,650 species
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.75,1:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有8650种鸟类，卡特先生{\r}\Nof birds in the world today, Mr. Carter.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.55,1:20:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}光是美国估计就有{\r}\NIt is estimated that 5,750,000,000 birds
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.43,1:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}五十七亿五千万只鸟{\r}\Nlive in the United States alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.43,1:20:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}世界五大洲…{\r}\NThe five continents of the world...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.43,1:21:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杀光它们！ 除掉这些麻烦的动物{\r}\NKill them all. Get rid of the messy animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.39,1:21:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}…可能就有超过一千亿只鸟{\r}\N...probably contain more than 100 billion birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.60,1:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 世界末日到了 - 那些海鸥一定是想吃鱼{\r}\NIt's the end of the world. Those gulls must have been after the fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.40,1:21:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 当然！ - 孩子们，快把饭吃完{\r}\NOf course! Hurry up, children. Finish your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.32,1:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈，鸟会吃掉我们吗？{\r}\NAre the birds gonna eat us, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.11,1:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们也许太过小题大做了{\r}\NHell, maybe we're all getting a little carried away by this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.95,1:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几只鸟确实很反常 但没理由相信…{\r}\NAdmittedly, a few birds did act strange, but that's no reason to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.37,1:21:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说过了，这不止是几只鸟 有海鸥、乌鸦、雨燕…{\r}\NI keep telling you, this isn't a few birds. These are gulls, crows, swifts...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.62,1:21:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没听说过 不同种类的鸟会聚集在一起{\r}\NI have never known birds of different species to flock together.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.92,1:21:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是无法想像的{\r}\NThe very concept is unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.51,1:21:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果真的发生了 我们根本没机会！{\r}\NWhy, if that happened, we wouldn't have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.80,1:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们怎么可能斗得过它们？{\r}\NHow could we possibly hope to fight them?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.14,1:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不可能赢 说得对，邦迪太太{\r}\NWe couldn't, you're right. You're right, Mrs. Bundy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.31,1:21:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}发生什么事了？{\r}\NWhat's the matter? Something wrong out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.56,1:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们正在打仗，山姆{\r}\NWe're fighting a war, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.18,1:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打仗？ 跟谁打？{\r}\NA war? Against who?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.73,1:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 跟鸟打！ - 真庆幸你们以为这很有趣{\r}\NAgainst birds! I'm glad you all think this is so amusing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.31,1:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们快把孩子们吓死了{\r}\NYou've frightened the children half out of their wits.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.07,1:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}若这位小姐说{\r}\NIf the young lady said
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.28,1:21:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她看见学生被攻击 你们为何不相信她？{\r}\Nshe saw the attack at a school, why don't you believe her?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.20,1:21:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 攻击？ 谁攻击学生了？ - 鸟、乌鸦{\r}\NWhat attack? Who attacked the school? Birds did. Crows.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.66,1:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们只顾着争辩！{\r}\NYou're all sitting around here debating!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.62,1:22:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们想它们接下来会怎样？ 撞破窗户？{\r}\NWhat do you want them to do next? Crash through that window?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.99,1:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈！ - 外套穿上{\r}\NMommy! Shh. Put on your coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.08,1:22:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们何不回家把门窗锁好？{\r}\NWhy don't you all go home, lock your doors and windows?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.46,1:22:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 到旧金山最快的路线是？ - 高速公路，女士{\r}\NWhat's the fastest way to San Francisco? The freeway, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.34,1:22:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么走？{\r}\NHow do I find it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.59,1:22:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也要去高速公路 可以跟着我{\r}\NI'm going out that way, lady. You can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.09,1:22:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那我们马上走吧 - 我的酒还没喝完{\r}\NWell, then let's leave now. Haven't finished my drink yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.85,1:22:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我尽快赶来了，凯西在哪里？{\r}\NI got here as fast as I could. Where's Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.85,1:22:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她跟安妮在一起，她没事 - 艾尔，学生被攻击时{\r}\NShe's with Annie. She's all right. Al, why aren't you over at the school,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.60,1:22:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么没赶到学校？{\r}\Nwhere the attack was?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.94,1:22:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我刚刚人在丹佛西特家{\r}\N'Cause I just got back from Dan Fawcett's place, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.19,1:22:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他昨晚被鸟杀死了 - 什么？{\r}\NHe was killed last night by birds. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.24,1:22:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}慢着，米契，你还不能确定{\r}\NNow, hold it, Mitch. You don't know that for a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.28,1:22:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马龙先生，事实是什么？{\r}\NWhat are the facts, Mr. Malone?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.45,1:22:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣塔罗沙警方认为是重罪谋杀{\r}\NThe Santa Rosa Police think it's a felony murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.91,1:22:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们认为是小偷闯进去杀了他{\r}\NThey think a burglar broke in, killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.91,1:22:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那满地的死鸟又该如何解释？{\r}\NHow do you explain the dead birds all over the floor?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.12,1:22:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣塔罗沙警方认为 鸟是在他被杀害后才飞进来的{\r}\NSanta Rosa Police figure they got in after the old man was killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.46,1:22:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣塔罗沙警方 今天有到学校去吗？{\r}\NWere the Santa Rosa Police at your school today?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.96,1:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要来吗？ - 冷静点，女士{\r}\NAre you coming? Now take it easy, lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.38,1:22:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里看不见一只鸟！{\r}\NThere isn't a bird anywhere in sight!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.05,1:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看天上的鸟 它们不播种也不收获{\r}\N"Look at the birds of the air. They do not sow or reap.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.89,1:23:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“但你们的天父喂养它们”{\r}\N"Yet your heavenly Father feeds them."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.64,1:23:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣塔克鲁兹 去年也发生了这种事{\r}\NSay, something like this happened in Santa Cruz last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.52,1:23:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海鸥遮盖了整座城镇{\r}\NThe town was just covered with seagulls.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.32,1:23:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 请快把你的酒喝完 - 没错，我想起来了{\r}\NWill you please finish your drink? That's right, sir. I recall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.94,1:23:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一大群海鸥在雾中迷路{\r}\NA large flock of seagulls got lost in a fog,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.53,1:23:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}朝着光线飞进了镇上{\r}\Nand headed into the town where all the lights were.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.24,1:23:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那也造成了不少麻烦 冲进建筑物里之类的{\r}\NThey made some mess, too, smashing into buildings and everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.54,1:23:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟就会制造麻烦{\r}\NThey always make a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.87,1:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}重点是没人为此感到不满{\r}\NThe point is that no one seemed to be upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.08,1:23:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们隔天早上就离开了 好像什么事都没发生一样{\r}\NThey were all gone next morning, just as though nothing at all had happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.59,1:23:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 可怜的东西 - 我要走了！你来不来？{\r}\NPoor things. I'm leaving! Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.92,1:23:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来了！{\r}\NAll right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.22,1:23:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望你们能搞清楚这件事！{\r}\NWell, hope you folks figure this thing out!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.60,1:23:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}世界末日到了！{\r}\NIt's the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.56,1:23:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我该回罐头工厂了 迪克，多少钱？{\r}\NI better get back to the cannery. What do I owe you, Deke?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.35,1:23:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}赛巴斯汀，等一下{\r}\NSebastian, hold it a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.14,1:23:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不想大惊小怪… - 没人说你是，米契{\r}\NI don't want to be an alarmist about this... No one ever said you were, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.11,1:23:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我们麻烦大了 我不知道这件事的起因{\r}\NI think we're in real trouble. I don't know how this started, or why,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.57,1:23:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我知道这是真的 我们不能不管{\r}\Nbut I know it's here and we'd be crazy to ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.86,1:23:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不管什么？  “鸟的战争”？ - 对，“鸟的战争”{\r}\NTo ignore what? The "bird war"? Yes, the "bird war."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.91,1:24:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟类攻击、瘟疫… 随怎么称呼{\r}\NThe bird attack, plague... Call it what you like,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.91,1:24:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们正在某处聚集 它们会回来的，我敢保证{\r}\Nthey're massing out there someplace, and they'll be back. You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.79,1:24:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 荒谬 - 过来一下{\r}\NRidiculous. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.12,1:24:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除非我们采取行动{\r}\NUnless we do something right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.62,1:24:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除非我们疏散博德加湾…{\r}\Nunless we get Bodega Bay on the move, they...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.29,1:24:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，米契{\r}\NLook, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.34,1:24:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就算这是真的，就算这些鸟…{\r}\NEven if this is true, even if all the birds...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.67,1:24:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不相信这是真的？ - 米契，我不相信{\r}\NDon't you believe it's true? No, Mitch, frankly I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.55,1:24:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这没道理… - 这确实发生了，还没道理吗？{\r}\NThere's no reason. I... Well, it's happening. Isn't that a reason?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.76,1:24:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我爱博德加湾… - 那就协助我{\r}\NI like Bodega Bay as well as the next man... Fine, then help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.31,1:24:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是镇上的要人 若你帮我，镇民都会听话{\r}\NYou're an important man in this town. If you help, they all will.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.73,1:24:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么帮？ 你想怎么做？{\r}\NHelp how? What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.02,1:24:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邦迪太太提到圣塔克鲁兹的事{\r}\NMrs. Bundy said something about Santa Cruz.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.02,1:24:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海鸥在雾中迷路 朝着光线飞去{\r}\NAbout seagulls getting lost in a fog and flying in towards the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.65,1:24:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这时节不会起雾！ - 那就用人工造雾！{\r}\NWe don't have fog this time of year! Make our own fog!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.99,1:24:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要怎么做？{\r}\NHow do you figure to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.03,1:24:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}学军队使用烟雾罐{\r}\NWe can use smoke pots, the way the Army uses them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.36,1:24:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们看！{\r}\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.16,1:24:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们又攻击了 梅兰妮，待在这里，走吧，艾尔！{\r}\NThey're attacking again. Melanie, you stay in here. Come on, Al!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.71,1:24:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小心！{\r}\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.74,1:25:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}汽油流了满地 那个男人在点烟！{\r}\NLook at the gas. That man's lighting a cigar!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.58,1:25:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿！听着！别把火柴丢地上！{\r}\NHey, you! Watch out! Don't drop that match!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.96,1:25:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快离开！{\r}\NGet out of there!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.33,1:25:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 先生，快跑！ - 小心！{\r}\N- Mister, run! - Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.63,1:25:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}注意！小心啊！{\r}\NLook out! Look out! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.18,1:26:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿！{\r}\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.39,1:28:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们为什么要这么做？{\r}\NWhy are they doing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.40,1:28:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们为什么要这么做？{\r}\NWhy are they doing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.69,1:28:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别人说在来了之后 整件事就开始了！{\r}\NThey said when you got here, the whole thing started!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.70,1:28:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是谁？ 是什么东西？{\r}\NWho are you? What are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.33,1:28:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从哪里来的？{\r}\NWhere did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.70,1:29:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为这都是造成的{\r}\NI think you're the cause of all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.08,1:29:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想是恶魔！恶魔！{\r}\NI think you're evil! Evil!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.09,1:29:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天啊！{\r}\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.89,1:29:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们离开了！{\r}\NI think they're going!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.31,1:29:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以去安妮家接凯西了{\r}\NWe can get Cathy at Annie's now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.09,1:29:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乌鸦又来了{\r}\N- The crows again. - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.27,1:30:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.55,1:30:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，待在这里{\r}\NOh, no. Stay here. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.06,1:30:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西！凯西在哪里？{\r}\NCathy! Where's Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.47,1:31:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，住手！{\r}\NMitch, don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.96,1:31:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别把她留在那里，米契{\r}\NOh, don't leave her there, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.52,1:32:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.39,1:33:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们送蜜雪儿回家后{\r}\NWhen we got back from taking Michele home,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.52,1:33:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们听见了爆炸声{\r}\Nwe heard the explosion
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.23,1:33:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就到外头查看{\r}\Nand we went outside to see what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.90,1:33:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟一下子聚集过来！{\r}\NAll at once the birds were everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.16,1:33:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她急忙把我推进屋里{\r}\NAll at once she pushed me inside,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.12,1:33:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟盖在她身上！{\r}\Nand they covered her!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.12,1:33:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮…她把我推进屋里！{\r}\NAnnie... She pushed me inside!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.10,1:34:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再给我一片木板{\r}\NGive me another one, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.15,1:34:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们在那边聚集多久了？{\r}\NHow long have they been gathering there?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.15,1:34:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大概15分钟{\r}\NOh, about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.91,1:34:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这似乎有个模式{\r}\NSeems like a pattern, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.62,1:34:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们攻击之后就消失 接着再开始聚集{\r}\NThey strike, then disappear, and then start massing again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.50,1:34:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看起来没什么不同，对吧？{\r}\NDoesn't look so very different, does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.05,1:34:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}像一阵烟笼罩着镇上…{\r}\NA little smoke hanging over the town, otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.55,1:34:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要再联络父亲吗？{\r}\NYou want to try your father again?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.93,1:34:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我刚刚试过了 电话不通{\r}\NNo, I tried a little while ago. The phone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.31,1:34:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 但我们还有电力吧？ - 有{\r}\N- Still got power, haven't we? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.93,1:34:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，电台传出消息了{\r}\NMitch, I'm getting something on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.94,1:34:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.07,1:35:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我收不到当地电台{\r}\NI can't get any of the local stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.41,1:35:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这应该是旧金山的电台{\r}\NI think this is San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.45,1:35:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“…和一组专业团队” 结束{\r}\N"...and the work of a team of professionals." End quote.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.04,1:35:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今早在博德加湾 有一大群乌鸦{\r}\NIn Bodega Bay early this morning, a large flock of crows
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.58,1:35:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}攻击因防火演习 而正在离校的学生{\r}\Nattacked a group of children who were leaving the school during a fire drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.13,1:35:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一位女孩因此受到重伤 被送往圣塔罗沙的医院{\r}\NOne little girl was seriously injured and taken to the hospital in Santa Rosa,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.71,1:35:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但多数学生都很平安{\r}\Nbut the majority of children reached safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.05,1:35:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们收到镇上 还有另一起攻击事件{\r}\NWe understand there was another attack on the town,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.51,1:35:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但资讯还不完全{\r}\Nbut this information is rather sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.76,1:35:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到目前为止 还没有消息指出{\r}\NSo far, no word has come through
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.76,1:35:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是否还有更多攻击事件{\r}\Nto show if there have been further attacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.35,1:35:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今日的国内新闻，华盛顿…{\r}\NOn the national scene today, in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.89,1:35:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就这样？{\r}\NWell, is that all?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.48,1:35:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我得再拿些木头进来 绝不能让火熄灭{\r}\NI'll have to get some more wood in. Mustn't let this fire go out.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.28,1:35:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 米契，你有封死阁楼的窗户吗？ - 都封好了{\r}\NDid you get the windows in the attic, Mitch? Yes, I got them all, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.99,1:35:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你觉得它们何时会攻击？ - 我不知道{\r}\NWhen do you think they'll come? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.32,1:35:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}若有更大型的鸟 它们会冲进屋子里的{\r}\NIf there are bigger birds, Mitch, they'll get into the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.45,1:35:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们只得冒这个险 - 也许我们该离开{\r}\NWell, it's just a chance we'll have to take. Maybe we ought to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.04,1:35:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在不行！ 它们正在外头聚集{\r}\NNo, not now! Not while they're massing out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.04,1:36:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那要何时？ - 我们再看看{\r}\NWhen? We'll just see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.46,1:36:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们要去哪？ - 我不知道{\r}\N- Where will we go? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.09,1:36:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}目前我们很安全{\r}\NI think we're safe here for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.38,1:36:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们去捡木头 - 木头烧光了怎么办？{\r}\NLet's get the wood in now. What happens when you run out of wood?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.84,1:36:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不知道！我们可以拆家具 - 你不知道！{\r}\NI don't know! We'll break up the furniture. You don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.59,1:36:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你何时才会知道？ 到时我们都死了！{\r}\NYou don't know! When will you know? When we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.55,1:36:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你爸在的话…{\r}\NIf only your father were here...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.35,1:36:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，米契{\r}\NI'm sorry. I'm sorry, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.61,1:36:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去煮点咖啡喝，好吗？{\r}\NMake yourself some coffee, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.36,1:36:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在假定总统的任务时{\r}\N"In assuming the tasks of the presidency,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.57,1:36:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“我认为少有世代…”{\r}\N"I said that few generations..."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.21,1:36:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 它们要去哪里？ - 内陆某处{\r}\NWhere are they heading? Somewhere inland.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.25,1:36:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 圣塔罗沙？ - 也许吧{\r}\NSanta Rosa? Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.59,1:36:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧，我们去捡木头{\r}\NCome on. Let's get the wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.59,1:37:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 米契，我能把爱情鸟拿进来吗？ - 不行！{\r}\NMitch? Can I bring the lovebirds in here? No!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.76,1:37:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈，它们在笼子里 - 它们也是鸟，不是吗？{\r}\NBut, Mom, they're in a cage. They're birds, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.39,1:37:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让它们待在厨房吧，亲爱的{\r}\NLet's leave them in the kitchen, huh, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.90,1:38:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，鸟为什么要这么做？{\r}\NMitch, why are they doing this, the birds?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.19,1:38:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们不知道，亲爱的 - 它们为什么要杀人？{\r}\NWe don't know, honey. Why are they trying to kill people?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.45,1:38:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望我知道原因{\r}\NI wish I could say.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.74,1:39:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不太舒服，梅兰妮{\r}\NI'm sick, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.57,1:40:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想… - 我陪去{\r}\NI want to... I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.27,1:44:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们走了{\r}\NThey're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.59,1:45:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契？{\r}\NMitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.27,1:48:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契！{\r}\NOh, Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.70,1:49:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}带凯西和莉迪雅离开这里{\r}\NGet Cathy and Lydia out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.21,1:49:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅兰妮！{\r}\NMelanie! Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.58,1:49:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.17,1:50:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可怜的东西！{\r}\NOh, poor thing! Poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.51,1:50:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去拿点水 绷带和消毒药水过来，快！{\r}\NListen, get some water, bandages, and antiseptic. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.81,1:50:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绷带，太可怕了{\r}\NBandages. It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.10,1:50:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西，拿白兰地过来{\r}\NCathy, get some brandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.53,1:50:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别怕！没事了{\r}\NNo, no, no! No, no, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.24,1:50:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了，没事了{\r}\NNo, it's all right, it's all right, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.25,1:50:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事了{\r}\NIt's all right. It's all right. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.28,1:51:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯西，拿油灯过来{\r}\NCathy, get the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.67,1:51:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们得送她去医院{\r}\NWe've got to get her to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.38,1:51:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不行，我们没地方可去 - 旧金山{\r}\NWe can't, Mitch. There's no place we can go. There's San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.26,1:51:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们撑不到那里 - 我们得试试{\r}\NWe'd never make it. We have to try.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.68,1:51:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们走海湾山路 就不必穿过镇上了{\r}\NWe'll go by way of Bay Hill Road. Then we don't have to go through town.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.85,1:51:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不能待在这里 她需要帮助！{\r}\NWe can't stay here. She needs help!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.43,1:51:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我好怕，非常害怕{\r}\NI'm frightened. Terribly frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.64,1:51:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道外面有什么东西{\r}\NI don't know what's outside there.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.77,1:51:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们最好在 下次攻击到来之前出发{\r}\NWe better get started before another attack comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.94,1:51:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们开梅兰妮的车 那会比开卡车快{\r}\NWe'll take Melanie's car. That'll be faster than the truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.78,1:51:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 能替她包扎好吗？ - 我尽量{\r}\NCan you finish the bandaging? I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.45,1:51:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.54,1:52:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契？ 用车上的收音机 听听有什么消息{\r}\NMitch? See if you can get anything on the car radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.33,1:54:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟类攻击事件目前已缓和{\r}\NThe bird attacks have subsided for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.96,1:54:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}博德加湾似乎是攻击的中心 虽然赛巴斯托波和圣塔罗沙{\r}\NBodega Bay seems to be the center, though there are reports of minor attacks
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.13,1:54:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也传出了轻微的攻击事件{\r}\Non Sebastopol and a few on Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.26,1:54:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}博德加湾周围已设满路障{\r}\NBodega Bay has been cordoned off by roadblocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.84,1:54:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多数的镇民已设法逃出{\r}\NMost of the townspeople have managed to get out,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.89,1:54:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但仍有少数居民受困{\r}\Nbut there are still some isolated pockets of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.80,1:54:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}至于下一步该怎么做 当局还没有决定{\r}\NNo decision has been arrived at yet as to what the next step will be,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.27,1:54:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但已有人开始讨论 是否该派军队进驻{\r}\Nbut there's been some discussion as to whether the military should go in.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.52,1:54:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸟类攻击似乎是阵歇性的{\r}\NIt appears that the bird attacks come in waves,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.27,1:54:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}中间的间隔时间很长{\r}\Nwith long intervals between.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.27,1:54:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}攻击原因目前还不明朗{\r}\NThe reason for this does not seem clear as yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.26,1:56:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有从电台上听到什么吗？{\r}\NDid you hear anything on the radio?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.39,1:56:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没关系，来吧{\r}\NIt's all right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.26,1:57:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，不要！{\r}\NNo. No!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.09,1:57:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契？{\r}\NMitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.47,1:57:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}待在那里{\r}\NStay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.72,1:57:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米契，我能带爱情鸟走吗？{\r}\NCan I bring the lovebirds, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.14,1:57:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它们没有伤害人{\r}\NThey haven't harmed anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.48,1:57:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，带着它们{\r}\NAll right. Bring them.

